description: Introducing the 2019 GMC Acadia SLT - a perfect blend of sophistication and practicality, designed to elevate your driving experience. This midsize SUV offers a spacious interior with seating for up to seven passengers, making it ideal for families and adventures alike. Under the hood, the Acadia SLT is powered by a robust 3.6L V6 engine, delivering a smooth yet powerful performance, while the advanced six-speed automatic transmission ensures an efficient ride. Equipped with All-Wheel Drive, you can confidently tackle various road conditions, providing peace of mind on any journey. The exterior exudes a commanding presence with its bold lines and distinctive grille, complemented by stylish alloy wheels. Inside, the Acadia boasts premium leather upholstery and a host of technology features, including a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, keeping you connected on the go. Safety is paramount, and the GMC Acadia SLT is equipped with a variety of advanced safety features such as lane-keeping assist, rear cross-traffic alert, and automatic emergency braking. Experience the perfect fusion of comfort, versatility, and safety with the 2019 GMC Acadia SLT. Your next adventure awaits!

description:
• The 2019 Land Rover Discovery Sport SE is a compact luxury sport utility vehicle with a stylish, rugged exterior that reflects Land Rover s off-road heritage.
  • It is powered by a turbocharged 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine producing about 237 horsepower and 251 lb-ft of torque, paired with a smooth nine-speed automatic transmission.
  • All-wheel drive (AWD) comes standard, helping it handle rain, snow, and light off-road terrain with confidence.
  • The SE trim seats five passengers comfortably with quality materials and available partial leather upholstery.
  • Front and rear passengers enjoy spacious headroom and legroom for a vehicle in this class.
  • A touchscreen infotainment system with Bluetooth, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration provides modern connectivity.
  • Standard safety and driver-assist features include traction control, a rearview camera, parking sensors, and multiple airbags.
  • Optional upgrades can add features like blind-spot monitoring, heated seats, and a panoramic sunroof for increased comfort.
  • The Discovery Sport s terrain response system and hill descent control enhance its capability off paved roads.
  • Cargo space is generous for its segment, and an optional third-row seat expands passenger capacity when needed.
  • Fuel economy is modest at around 21 mpg city/25 mpg highway, typical of premium small SUVs.
  • Its ride quality balances on-road comfort with a firm suspension tuned for capable handling.
  • Many owners appreciate the Discovery Sport s upscale styling and overall versatility, though some note that technology features can feel dated compared with rivals.
  • Reliability ratings are mixed, and maintenance costs can be higher than average for this class.
  • Overall, the 2019 Discovery Sport SE blends luxury, practicality, and off-road ability, making it a compelling choice for buyers seeking a premium SUV with adventurous capability.

description: Feel the thrill of driving the 2019 Kia Sorento SX V6, where performance meets comfort. With a powerful 3.3L GDI Dual CVVT DOHC 24-Valve V6 engine generating an impressive 290 horsepower at 6400 rpm, every journey feels dynamic. This front-wheel drive SUV is designed for those who love versatility and style. The sleek Platinum Graphite exterior complements the spacious interior adorned with light gray leather seats, creating a refined ambiance for all passengers. The Sorento is packed with modern features that enhance both safety and convenience. Enjoy the benefits of adaptive cruise control, lane departure warning, and blind-spot monitoring, ensuring peace of mind on every trip. The hands-free liftgate simplifies loading and unloading your gear. Your entertainment needs are covered with smart device integration, Bluetooth connectivity, and satellite radio options for enjoyable road trips or daily commutes. Navigate effortlessly to your destinations using the advanced navigation system while enjoying heated front seats during colder months. With a fuel economy rating of 19 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, this vehicle strikes the right balance between power and efficiency. Experience all these amazing options while cruising down the road or tackling any adventurous weekend getaway.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front and side impact airbags, OnStar emergency communication, and a rearview camera to give you peace of mind on the road.

This 2019 Chevrolet Trax LT is the perfect blend of style, capability, and technology. With its impressive list of features and the confidence of a local trade-in, this SUV is ready to take your driving experience to new heights. Visit our showroom today and discover how this Trax can elevate your daily commute or weekend adventures.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability and comfort in the 2019 Jeep Compass Trailhawk. This versatile SUV is ready to take on any adventure, whether you're navigating rugged terrain or cruising down the highway.

Boasting a powerful 2.4L I4 engine paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and 4WD, the Compass Trailhawk delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 22 MPG in the city and 30 MPG on the highway.

Standout features include:

• GPS Navigation
• Bluetooth® Integrated Voice Command
• Bluetooth® Streaming Audio
• HD Radio
• Media Hub (USB, AUX)
• Uconnect 4C Nav with 8.4" Display
• Security Alarm
• Remote Start System
• Power Liftgate
• Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection
• ParkSense Rear Park Assist System
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated Front Seats

The Compass Trailhawk also comes equipped with the Cold Weather Group and Safety & Security Group, ensuring your comfort and peace of mind no matter the conditions.

Elevate your driving experience with the advanced technology and premium amenities of the 2019 Jeep Compass Trailhawk. This SUV is the perfect blend of capability, convenience, and style, ready to take you wherever the road or trail may lead.

With its striking White exterior and well-appointed interior, the Compass Trailhawk is sure to turn heads. The spacious cabin and versatile cargo area provide ample room for your passengers and gear, making it the ideal companion for your next adventure.

Discover the ultimate in Jeep performance and refinement. Visit our showroom today to experience the 2019 Compass Trailhawk for yourself and see why it's the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility in this 2019 Chevrolet Trax LS. With its striking blue exterior and well-appointed interior, this compact SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Visit our Website for a Complimentary CarFax Report!!!
• Local Trade
• Great Service History
• 3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Coverage
• Auto Reward Program
• Premium audio system: Chevrolet MyLink
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Fully automatic headlights
• All-Wheel Drive Chassis
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• 2-Way Manual Front Passenger Seat Adjuster

Powered by the efficient ECOTEC 1.4L I4 SMPI DOHC Turbocharged VVT engine, this Trax delivers a responsive and fuel-efficient ride, achieving an impressive 24 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway. The 6-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel-drive system provide a confident and composed driving experience, whether navigating city streets or tackling light off-road adventures.

Inside, the Trax LS offers a wealth of features designed to enhance your daily commute and weekend getaways. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 System with 6-speaker audio, dual-zone climate control, and power windows ensure your comfort and convenience. Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual-stage airbags, electronic stability control, and OnStar emergency communication system.

This Trax is a Triton Certified Classic Vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and comes with a 5-day return/30-day exchange policy, giving you the peace of mind you deserve. With its impressive combination of style, performance, and features, this 2019 Chevrolet Trax LS is an exceptional value that's sure to impress.

Whether you're shopping for a car, truck, or SUV, we deliver unbeatable variety, trusted service, and fast, flexible financing. Proudly serving Harrisburg, Carlisle, Camp Hill, and beyond—discover why more drivers choose Fred Beans.

description:
Discover the ultimate driving experience with this stunning 2019 Ford Edge Titanium. This SUV is a true testament to Ford's commitment to innovation and performance, offering a captivating blend of style, technology, and capability.

Boasting a host of premium features, this Edge Titanium is equipped to elevate your driving pleasure. Highlights include:

• FORD CO-PILOT360 ASSIST+: Evasive Steering Assist, Voice-Activated Touchscreen Navigation System, and SiriusXM Traffic & Travel Link
• Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go
• Lane Centering
• White Platinum Metallic Tri-Coat exterior
• COLD WEATHER PACKAGE: Front & Rear Floor Liners, Windshield Wiper De-Icer, Heated Steering Wheel

Powered by the responsive EcoBoost 2.0L I4 engine and mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission, this all-wheel-drive Edge delivers an exceptional driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 21 mpg in the city and 28 mpg on the highway, you'll enjoy impressive fuel efficiency without sacrificing performance.

Step inside and be captivated by the refined interior, featuring premium leather-trimmed heated sport bucket seats, a voice-activated touchscreen navigation system, and a stunning B&O sound system by Bang & Olufsen. The spacious cabin and versatile cargo area make this Edge Titanium the perfect companion for your daily commute, weekend adventures, and everything in between.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Ford Co-Pilot360, Evasive Steering Assist, and a suite of advanced airbags providing you and your loved ones with the utmost protection.

This exceptional 2019 Ford Edge Titanium is available now for $14,988. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can enhance your driving lifestyle.

This stunning SUV combines sleek design, advanced technology, and powerful driving dynamics for an unparalleled driving experience. With extra spacing in the interior, you and your passengers will have plenty of room to stretch out and enjoy the ride. The spacious cargo area provides ample storage for all your adventures, making this vehicle perfect for both daily commutes and weekend getaways. Under the hood, the X3 sDrive30i boasts a 2.0-liter TwinPower Turbo inline 4-cylinder engine, delivering an impressive 248 horsepower. Visit your local dealership today and experience the ultimate driving machine for yourself.

Comfort
  • The steering wheel rim is heated.
  • Heated seats offer cool weather comfort by warming the seat quickly, before the air in the passenger compartment is fully warmed by the heater.
  • The seating surfaces are covered in leather.
Convenience
  • Access to the cargo area is gained via a large, power-operated rear door that opens upwards. This door may also contain the rear windshield of the vehicle.
  • The keyfob has the ability to remotely start the vehicle.
Safety and Security
  • A blind spot detection system will alert the driver when another vehicle is within the warning zone.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
  • Otherwise known as Bluetooth, this technology allows electronic devices to integrate with the vehicle systems without the need for a physical connection between them.

description:
2019 Chevrolet Equinox LT Vehicle DescriptionIntroductionThe 2019 Chevrolet Equinox LT is a well-rounded compact SUV that blends comfort, capability, and modern technology into a versatile package suited for daily driving, family outings, and weekend adventures. Positioned above the base trim, the LT adds desirable features and comfort enhancements that elevate the overall driving experience. With a spacious interior, refined styling, and confident performance, the Equinox LT delivers a balanced ride that s both practical and enjoyable. Whether navigating busy city streets or cruising on the highway, this SUV offers reliability, convenience, and comfort for every journey.Performance
  • Engine: 1.5-liter turbocharged 4-cylinder
  • Horsepower: 170 hp
  • Torque: 203 lb-ft
  • Transmission: 6-speed automatic
  • Drivetrain: All-Wheel Drive (AWD)
  • Fuel Economy: Efficient for daily commuting and highway travel
  • Suspension tuned for smooth ride quality
The 2019 Equinox LT s turbocharged engine provides a lively yet efficient performance that balances responsive acceleration with fuel-saving capability. The 6-speed automatic transmission shifts smoothly, helping deliver comfortable driving dynamics whether you re cruising around town or heading out on longer routes. With available AWD, this SUV can offer enhanced traction on slippery surfaces or varied road conditions, making it a capable choice for drivers in all seasons.This performance setup offers a confident and composed ride that gives drivers peace of mind while navigating both urban and rural environments, without sacrificing everyday practicality or efficiency.Interior & Comfort
  • Seating Capacity: 5 passengers
  • Premium cloth seating surfaces
  • Dual-zone automatic climate control
  • Power driver s seat with adjustable lumbar support
  • Leather-wrapped steering wheel with mounted controls
  • Chevrolet Infotainment System with touchscreen display
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility
  • Bluetooth hands-free connectivity and USB ports
  • Rear 60/40 split-folding seats for flexible cargo space
Inside, the Equinox LT welcomes passengers with a comfortable and user-friendly cabin. The seats provide supportive comfort for both short trips and long drives, while dual-zone climate control helps keep everyone comfortable in changing weather. The intuitive infotainment system with smartphone integration keeps connectivity and entertainment front and center, and ample storage compartments help keep the interior organized. With flexible rear seating and plenty of passenger room, the Equinox LT s cabin is designed to accommodate both people and cargo with ease.The interior balance of comfort and practicality makes every journey from daily commuting to family road trips relaxed and enjoyable for all occupants.Dimensions & Capacity
  • Wheelbase: Well-balanced for stability and interior space
  • Overall Length: Compact SUV proportions with generous cabin room
  • Width: Comfortable interior width for passengers
  • Height: Elevated for confident visibility
  • Passenger Volume: Spacious seating for five occupants
  • Cargo Volume: Competitive rear cargo space with rear seats folded
The 2019 Equinox LT s dimensions help create an interior that feels open and accommodating without being cumbersome on the road. Its cargo area is generous for the class, allowing room for luggage, groceries, sports gear, or other essentials. The easy-to-use 60/40 rear seat split further expands flexibility for both passengers and cargo, making the SUV practical for a wide range of lifestyles and activities.Exterior Features
  • Refined and modern SUV styling
  • Signature Chevrolet grille with bold design cues
  • LED daytime running lights
  • Alloy wheels with polished finish
  • Body-color side mirrors and trim accents
  • Roof rails for added cargo utility
  • Rear spoiler and sleek profile
The exterior of the Equinox LT presents a confident and contemporary look that fits a variety of settings from suburban streets to outdoor adventures. Clean lines, defined body surfaces, and thoughtful styling details give this SUV a visual appeal that stands out in its segment. Practical exterior features like roof rails enhance functionality without detracting from the overall aesthetic.Safety & Driver Assistance
  • Standard advanced airbag system
  • Anti-lock Braking System (ABS)
  • Electronic Stability Control and Traction Control
  • Rearview camera for added confidence while reversing
  • Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS)
  • Available advanced driver-assist features depending on package
Safety is a foundational part of the 2019 Equinox LT s design. With a range of standard protective systems and the potential for additional driver-assist features depending on equipment, this SUV helps enhance driver awareness and passenger protection. Whether navigating urban traffic or cruising on highways, these systems contribute to a secure and confident driving experience.SummaryThe 2019 Chevrolet Equinox LT is a versatile and well-equipped compact SUV that appeals to drivers who want a balanced blend of comfort, capability, and everyday practicality. Its turbocharged engine and smooth automatic transmission provide responsive performance and solid fuel efficiency, while the comfortable interior and intuitive technology features keep passengers connected and content. Thoughtful cargo flexibility and a spacious cabin make it a reliable choice for families, daily commuters, or weekend adventurers alike. With stylish exterior design and a strong safety foundation, the Equinox LT delivers a confident and enjoyable ride that fits a wide range of lifestyles. Whether you re running errands, heading out on a road trip, or navigating suburban roads, the 2019 Equinox LT offers a well-rounded, dependable SUV experience mile after mile.

2019 Buick Encore Preferred Vehicle DescriptionIntroductionThe 2019 Buick Encore Preferred is a refined and versatile subcompact SUV that blends smart design, comfortable amenities, and everyday practicality. As one of Buick s most popular models, the Encore delivers an inviting driving experience with a confident presence on the road and a cabin that maximizes space without sacrificing style. The Preferred trim enhances the experience with popular comfort and technology features that appeal to a wide range of drivers from daily commuters to weekend adventurers. With its efficient performance, thoughtful interior layout, and a premium feel, the 2019 Buick Encore Preferred stands out as a well-rounded choice in the compact SUV segment.Performance
  • Engine: 1.4-liter turbocharged 4-cylinder
  • Horsepower: 138 hp
  • Torque: 148 lb-ft
  • Transmission: 6-speed automatic
  • Drivetrain: Front-Wheel Drive (FWD)
  • Suspension tuned for smooth ride quality
  • Fuel economy engineered for daily driving and highway cruising
The 2019 Encore Preferred s turbocharged engine provides responsive acceleration and a confident feel in city traffic and on the open road. Its smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission keeps the engine in an efficient power range, helping balance performance and fuel economy. With the available AWD system, this SUV offers enhanced traction and control in varying weather conditions, giving drivers extra confidence on rainy or slippery roads.This performance setup delivers a composed and enjoyable ride that s perfect for both urban commuting and longer highway trips. The engine s lively response and the suspension s refined tuning work together to make every journey feel effortless and assured.Interior & Comfort
  • Seating for 5 passengers
  • Premium cloth upholstery with comfortable support
  • Dual-zone automatic climate control
  • Power driver s seat for added comfort and customization
  • Buick Infotainment System with touchscreen display
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
  • Bluetooth connectivity and USB ports
  • Thoughtful storage compartments and intuitive controls
Inside, the Buick Encore Preferred offers a welcoming and functional environment for both driver and passengers. The seating is supportive and comfortable, making it easy to settle in for daily commutes or long highway journeys. Dual-zone climate control allows personalized comfort for all occupants, while the infotainment system with smartphone integration keeps connectivity and entertainment at your fingertips. The ergonomic layout and practical storage solutions help make the cabin both convenient and pleasant.With its refined materials and well-designed interior, the Encore feels more upscale than its compact footprint might suggest.Dimensions & Capacity
  • Wheelbase: Balanced for interior space and maneuverability
  • Overall Length: Compact for easy parking and urban driving
  • Width: Comfortable cabin space for passengers
  • Height: Elevated SUV stance with good headroom
  • Passenger Capacity: 5 passengers
  • Cargo Volume: Flexible space with rear seats folded
The 2019 Buick Encore Preferred s compact size makes it easy to navigate and park in crowded city streets while still providing generous interior room for passengers. The smart design of the cargo area and folding rear seats enhances versatility, allowing you to adapt space for luggage, groceries, or gear with ease. This thoughtful use of space ensures that the Encore combines practicality with everyday comfort.Exterior Features
  • Sophisticated Buick exterior styling with signature grille
  • Halogen projector headlamps
  • 18-inch alloy wheels with clean design
  • Body-color side mirrors and door handles
  • Roof rails for additional cargo possibilities
  • Elevated stance and refined profile
The exterior of the Encore Preferred conveys style and urban confidence. Its refined design language, premium trim details, and available roof rails contribute to a look that s both modern and practical. These visual elements help the Encore stand out on the road while also providing functional benefits for everyday use and weekend adventures.Safety & Driver Assistance
  • Standard safety features including advanced airbags
  • Anti-lock braking system (ABS)
  • Stability and traction control
  • Rearview camera for confident reversing
  • Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS)
  • Available driver-assist features depending on options and package
Safety is an integral part of the Encore Preferred s design. The suite of standard safety systems helps enhance driver awareness and protect occupants in various road conditions. From stability control to advanced restraint technology, the Encore delivers peace of mind for you and your passengers.SummaryThe 2019 Buick Encore Preferred is a well-rounded subcompact SUV that brings together comfortable seating, efficient performance, and modern technology in a versatile package. Its turbocharged engine, smooth ride quality, and intuitive features make it an enjoyable vehicle for everyday driving and longer journeys alike. The thoughtfully designed interior offers comfort and connectivity, while the refined exterior styling gives it a confident presence on the road. With strong safety and driver-assist features, the Encore Preferred provides both peace of mind and practicality making it an excellent choice for drivers who want a compact SUV that is stylish, comfortable, and capable in everyday life. This model delivers a balanced and rewarding driving experience mile after mile.

Discover the exceptional 2019 Jaguar F-PACE 25t Premium, a captivating blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This stunning SUV is poised to elevate your driving experience and turn heads wherever you go.

Boasting an array of premium features, the F-PACE 25t Premium is a true standout in its class. Highlights include:

• Basic Rear Seat Convenience Package
• Cold Climate Package

Step inside and be captivated by the Meridian 380W Sound System, which delivers a concert-hall-quality audio experience. Dual-zone automatic climate control, heated front and rear seats, and a heated steering wheel ensure your comfort in any weather. Safety and technology are also at the forefront, with features like Adaptive Cruise Control, High-Speed Emergency Braking, and a comprehensive suite of driver-assist systems. The InControl Pro Services and Wi-Fi Hotspot keep you connected and in control, no matter where your adventures take you.

This meticulously maintained F-PACE 25t Premium is a true testament to Jaguar's commitment to craftsmanship and innovation. With its stunning white exterior and well-appointed interior, it's a vehicle that commands attention and delivers an unparalleled driving experience.

Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures. description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2019 Subaru Forester Touring. Boasting a sleek gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this one-owner vehicle is packed with advanced features that will captivate the discerning driver.

• NAVIGATION
• EYE SIGHT TECHNOLOGY
• LANE KEEP
• REAR CROSS TRAFFIC ALERT
• BLIND SPOT TECHNOLOGY
• ADAPTIVE CRUISE CONTROL
• POWER REAR TAIL GATE
• LED STEERING RESPONSIVE HEADLIGHTS WITH HIGH BEAM ASSIST
• APPLE CAR PLAY!
• PUSH BUTTON START
• HEATED FRONT SEATS
• HEATED LEATHER SEATS
• HEATED FRONT AND REAR SEATS
• HEATED STEERING WHEEL

The Forester Touring's impressive 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine, paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 26 city/33 highway MPG, this SUV offers impressive fuel economy without sacrificing performance.

Elevate your driving experience with the Forester Touring's premium features, including a panoramic moonroof, power liftgate, and the advanced Starlink multimedia system with navigation and Apple CarPlay. The Harman Kardon premium audio system will immerse you in rich, high-quality sound, while the adaptive cruise control and lane-keep assist technologies provide added peace of mind on the road.

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, the Forester Touring boasts heated front and rear seats, a heated steering wheel, and dual-zone automatic climate control. The perforated leather-trimmed upholstery and power-adjustable driver's seat ensure a tailored fit for every journey.

Safety is a top priority in the Forester Touring, with advanced features like the EyeSight driver-assist technology, blind-spot detection, and rear cross-traffic alert. You can navigate with confidence, knowing that your vehicle is equipped to keep you and your loved ones secure.

This exceptional Subaru Forester Touring is a must-see for the discerning buyer. Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance that will elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this vehicle is the perfect choice for your next adventure.

Coated in the elegant Deep Black Pearl, this Tiguan SEL combines European sophistication with the utility needed for Northern Virginia commuting. Featuring a 2.0L turbocharged engine and a responsive 8-speed automatic transmission, it offers a smooth, confident ride whether youre navigating the Capital Beltway or parking in the tight streets of Georgetown., The SEL trim is a tech-lover's dream, highlighted by the stunning Volkswagen Digital Cockpita fully digital, high-resolution instrument cluster that replaces traditional gauges. Local drivers will especially appreciate the Power Tilting and Sliding Panoramic Sunroof and the convenience of Remote Engine Start, allowing you to warm up the vehicle before stepping out into a brisk Maryland morning., Inside, the cabin is refined with Titan Black Perforated V-Tex Leatherette seating and Heated Front Comfort Seats, providing a luxury feel that is also durable and easy to clean. Safety is paramount in the DC metro area, and this Tiguan is fully equipped with Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC), Blind Spot Monitor, and Park Distance Control (front and rear sensors) to make urban driving effortless. The inclusion of the Rear Roof-Edge Spoiler and 18-inch two-tone alloy wheels adds a sporty, modern touch to its sophisticated profile., This 2019 Tiguan SEL is an exceptional value for families and professionals alike, offering more cargo space and standard features than many of its competitors. description:
2019 Nissan Rogue Sport S Sport Utility 4D The 2019 Nissan Rogue Sport S is a compact crossover SUV that offers a stylish design, comfortable ride, and practical features for urban driving and light adventure. With efficient fuel economy, advanced safety technologies, and a spacious interior, the Rogue Sport S is a solid choice for commuters and small families.Performance & Powertrain
  • Engine: 2.0L 4-cylinder DOHC 16-valve
  • Horsepower: 141 hp @ 6,000 rpm
  • Torque: 147 lb-ft @ 4,400 rpm
  • Drivetrain: Front-Wheel Drive (FWD) or available Intelligent All-Wheel Drive (AWD)
  • Transmission: Xtronic CVT (Continuously Variable Transmission)Fuel Economy (AWD):
    • City: ~24 MPG
    • Highway: ~30 MPG
    • Combined: ~27 MPG
  • Fuel Tank Capacity: 14.5 gallons
  • Towing Capacity: Up to 1,102 lbs
Exterior Features
  • Wheels: 16-inch steel wheels with covers
  • Lighting: Halogen headlights with LED daytime running lights
  • Roof Rails: Available for extra cargo options
  • Rear Spoiler: Sporty rear design for aerodynamics
  • Body Design: Modern, sculpted lines with Nissan s signature V-Motion grille
  • Ground Clearance: 7.4 inches (AWD model)
Interior & Comfort
  • Seating Capacity: 5 passengers
  • Upholstery: Cloth-trimmed seats
  • Front Seats: 6-way manual-adjustable driver s seat
  • Rear Seats: 60/40 split-folding rear seats for extra cargo space
  • Climate Control: Manual air conditioning
  • Steering Wheel: Tilt and telescopic with integrated audio and cruise controls
  • Cargo Space:
    • 22.9 cu. ft. behind second row
    • 61.1 cu. ft. with rear seats folded
Technology & Infotainment
  • Infotainment System: 7-inch touchscreen display
  • Smartphone Integration: Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
  • Audio System: 4-speaker system
  • Bluetooth Hands-Free Phone System
  • USB & AUX Ports
  • Siri Eyes Free Voice Recognition
Safety & Driver AssistanceThe Nissan Safety Shield 360 comes standard, including:
  • Automatic Emergency Braking with Pedestrian Detection
  • Blind Spot Warning
  • Rear Cross Traffic Alert
  • Lane Departure Warning
  • Intelligent Forward Collision Warning
  • Rearview Camera
Cargo & Utility Features
  • Divide-N-Hide Cargo System (Optional)
  • Underfloor Storage Compartments
  • Available Power Liftgate
The 2019 Nissan Rogue Sport S is a practical and stylish compact SUV with great fuel efficiency, modern tech, and advanced safety features. It s an excellent option for those looking for an affordable and reliable crossover with everyday versatility.

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance with this 2019 Mazda CX-3 Sport. This compact crossover SUV is a true standout, offering a captivating design, a wealth of advanced features, and exceptional efficiency to elevate your driving experience.

Highlighted by its striking Blue exterior, the CX-3 Sport commands attention on the road. But its appeal goes far beyond its good looks. This vehicle is equipped with a robust SKYACTIV®-G 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, delivering an impressive 29 city/34 highway MPG to keep you moving with confidence.

• BLUETOOTH
• SPORT i-ACTIVSENSE PACKAGE
- Advanced Smart City Brake Support w/Pedestrian Det
- Mazda Radar Cruise Control (MRCC) with stop and go function
- Active Driving Display
- Automatic Climate Control
- Automatic Rain-Sensing Windshield Wipers
- Smart Brake Support System w/Collision Warning
- Lane Departure Warning (LDW)
- High Beam Control (HBC)
- LED Headlights & Taillights with auto leveling
- Auto Headlights (On/Off)
- Adaptive Front Lighting System (AFS)

Slip behind the wheel and experience the CX-3's exceptional handling and responsive performance, thanks to its 6-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive. The Sport i-ACTIVSENSE Package elevates the driving dynamics with advanced safety and convenience features, including Mazda Radar Cruise Control, Smart Brake Support, and Lane Departure Warning.

Inside, the CX-3 Sport offers a well-appointed cabin with thoughtful amenities to enhance your daily commute and weekend adventures. Enjoy the convenience of a Backup Camera, Infotainment System Voice Command, and Automatic Climate Control. The 6-speaker audio system, with features like Aha Internet Radio and Pandora, keeps you connected and entertained.

Whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the open road, the 2019 Mazda CX-3 Sport is the perfect companion. With its dynamic performance, comprehensive safety technologies, and impressive array of features, this crossover is a true standout in its class. Experience the difference for yourself - schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving the CX-3 Sport.

Elevate Your Driving Experience with this Stunning 2019 Subaru Ascent Limited

Introducing the 2019 Subaru Ascent Limited, a true masterpiece of engineering and design. This exceptional SUV is poised to elevate your driving experience to new heights, offering a captivating blend of power, versatility, and unparalleled comfort.

• Spacious and Versatile: With seating for up to 8 passengers and a generous cargo capacity, the Ascent Limited is the perfect companion for your family adventures. The split-folding rear seats and power liftgate make loading and unloading a breeze.
• Exceptional Performance: Equipped with a 2.4L DOHC Lineartronic CVT engine and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, this Ascent delivers a confident and responsive driving experience, regardless of the terrain.
• Refined Luxury: Step inside and be enveloped in the Ascent's premium Perforated Leather-Trimmed Upholstery, complemented by a host of luxury features, including Heated Front Bucket Seats, a Heated Steering Wheel, and a Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Plus System.
• Advanced Safety: Subaru's commitment to your well-being is evident in the Ascent's comprehensive suite of safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and an Emergency Communication System.
• Exceptional Efficiency: With an EPA-estimated 20 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, the Ascent Limited offers impressive fuel economy, ensuring you can go the distance without compromise.

Experience the ultimate in versatility, performance, and luxury with this 2019 Subaru Ascent Limited. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can enhance your driving experience and elevate your lifestyle.

description:
1982 Jeep Wagoneer 4x4

Introducing this 1982 Jeep Wagoneer 4X4 finished in Copper Metallic with classic faux woodgrain molding, paired with a black interior. This Wagoneer represents a straightforward example of one of Jeep's most recognizable full-size SUVs, offering vintage style and practical capability in a no-nonsense package.

Highlights:
- Copper Metallic Exterior Color
- Automatic Transmission
- V8 Engine
- Motorcraft Carburetor
- Power Steering
- Air Conditioining
- Bench Seating
- Roof Rack
- Electric Tailgate Window
- Manufacturer's Literature Included

Power comes from a V8 engine mated to an automatic transmission with column shift, delivering the optimal performance these full-size Jeeps are known for. The four-wheel-drive system adds versatility, while power steering, a Motorcraft carburetor, and a single exhaust outlet contribute to a simple, functional driving experience. Exterior details include Wagoneer badging, chrome trim and bumpers, white-line tires, and 15-inch steel wheels with Jeep-branded center caps.

Inside, the Wagoneer offers a spacious cabin with plenty of room for passengers and cargo, making it well-suited for daily use or weekend trips. Features include air conditioning, manual crank windows, a driver-side rearview mirror, a roof rack, a 3-spoke steering wheel, vent windows, and an AM/FM radio. The vehicle also includes the owner's manual and receipt copies.

The Jeep Wagoneer was one of the first SUVs to blend true four-wheel-drive capability with luxury-style comfort, helping set the blueprint for modern SUVs decades before they became mainstream. This Jeep Wagoneer 4x4 retains its classic character and is mechanically sound. For $14,750

Versatile and accommodating, the Accord's split-folding rear seats and ample cargo space make it the perfect companion for your daily commute, weekend getaways, and everything in between. The four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensitive steering ensure a smooth, responsive ride, no matter the road conditions.

With its impressive list of features, exceptional fuel efficiency, and Honda's renowned reliability, this 2023 Accord EX is an exceptional value at just $23,642. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional vehicle.

description: Introducing a beautifully maintained 2007 Lexus RX 400h AWD finished in the elegant Neptune Blue Mica exterior with a bright Ivory leather interior — a classic combination that still turns heads. This RX 400h brings together Lexus luxury, well-engineered hybrid performance, and outstanding real-world efficiency in a refined midsize crossover that remains exceptionally practical and comfortable today. Powertrain and Efficiency Under the hood sits the renowned 3.3L V6 hybrid system paired with Lexus’ electric drive components, delivering a combined 268 horsepower and the smooth, immediate response associated with hybrid torque delivery. The full-time all-wheel-drive system provides extra traction and confidence in a variety of driving conditions, while the electronic continuously variable-style hybrid transmission contributes to seamless acceleration. This specific vehicle has below 136,000 miles — averaging less than 7,000 miles per year — and consistently posts excellent fuel economy for its class: an EPA-style rating of approximately 27 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway. That makes this RX 400h a great choice for both daily commuting and longer highway trips where the hybrid system’s efficiency shines. Condition and History This vehicle is in excellent overall condition and presents extremely well inside and out. The Neptune Blue Mica paint retains a deep, glossy finish and pairs beautifully with the Ivory leather interior, which presents a bright, inviting cabin atmosphere that feels both modern and timeless. The car has a clean CARFAX report — a reassuring sign of responsible ownership and well-documented maintenance. Factory Default Features — Detailed Overview This 2007 RX 400h was built to offer a refined and feature-rich ownership experience right from the factory. Below is a detailed look at the factory-default features you’ll enjoy: Exterior and Convenience - Distinctive Neptune Blue Mica paint with a premium clearcoat finish for depth and durability. - Halogen projector-beam headlamps with auto-on/off function to enhance nighttime visibility. - Integrated fog lamps for improved low-visibility driving. - Power-folding side mirrors with body-color finish and integrated turn indicators on many factory configurations. - Power liftgate for convenient hands-free loading and unloading of cargo. - Roof rails for flexible cargo-carrying options (cross bars available as accessories). - Lightweight alloy wheels that combine a polished look with strong performance characteristics and help to reduce unsprung weight. Interior Comfort and Convenience - Ivory leather-trimmed seating that offers a luxurious feel and a bright, airy interior ambiance. The seats are supportive for long drives and easy to maintain. - Power-adjustable front seats with driver memory settings to store preferred seating and mirror positions. - Heated front seats to provide quick warmth on chilly mornings. - Split-folding 60/40 rear seats that fold flat to expand cargo capacity and make the cabin versatile for passengers and gear. - Dual-zone automatic climate control to keep driver and front passenger comfortable with individually controlled temperatures. - Power windows, power door locks, and remote keyless entry for everyday convenience. - Tilt-and-telescoping steering column for personalized driving ergonomics. - Multifunction steering wheel controls for audio and cruise control, enabling safer, more convenient operation while driving. - Interior woodgrain and metallic trim accents that add a touch of upscale styling and warmth to the cabin. Audio and Connectivity - A premium factory audio system tuned by Lexus to provide clear, balanced sound throughout the cabin. description:
2007 Land Rover LR3 V8 SE 4WD | 4.4L V8 | Silver Exterior | Black Interior

Experience legendary Land Rover capability and timeless utility in this 2007 Land Rover LR3 V8 SE, now available at our Land Rover dealership in Livermore, California. Finished in classic Silver with a Black interior, this LR3 represents one of the most durable and capable full-size SUVs Land Rover has ever produced—engineered to perform both on-road and off the beaten path.

Power comes from a proven 4.4L V8 engine paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission with CommandShift, delivering strong performance and smooth shifting. The full-time 4WD system, combined with Land Rover’s renowned Terrain Response system, provides confidence across a wide range of driving conditions, from daily commuting to off-road adventures.

With approximately 89,124 miles, this LR3 V8 SE stands out as a well-kept example of a highly respected Land Rover platform known for its versatility, mechanical strength, and commanding presence.

Notable Features & Equipment:

• V8 SE Trim Level
• Full-Time 4WD with Low-Range Transfer Case
• Terrain Response System
• Electronic Air Suspension
• Hill Descent Control (HDC)
• Dynamic Stability Control (DSC)
• Leather Seating Surfaces
• Power-Adjustable Front Seats
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Cruise Control
• Split-Folding Rear Seats
• Steering Wheel–Mounted Controls
• Power Windows, Locks, and Mirrors

Safety & Control:

• Anti-Lock Braking System (ABS)
• Traction Control
• Front, Side, and Curtain Airbags
• Tire Pressure Monitoring System
• Child Safety Locks & LATCH System

Exterior Highlights:

• 18-Inch Alloy Wheels
• Roof Rails
• Privacy Glass
• Front Fog Lights
• Rear Window Wiper
• Full-Size Spare Tire

If you’re searching for a used Land Rover LR3 V8, a capable 4WD SUV, or a classic Land Rover with proven off-road engineering, this LR3 delivers authentic capability and long-term value.

Buy With Confidence

We are a trusted Land Rover dealership located in Livermore, California, proudly serving the Tri-Valley, Bay Area, and customers nationwide. Every pre-owned vehicle is carefully inspected for quality, reliability, and overall condition, ensuring confidence with every purchase.

Nationwide Sales Available

Not located in California? No problem. We regularly complete out-of-state transactions and can assist with remote paperwork, financing options, and vehicle delivery to buyers in any state. Our experienced team makes purchasing simple and transparent, no matter where you’re located.

Contact us today for additional information, personalized photos or videos, or to schedule your test drive.

description: We bought this a couple of years ago from a guy on the east side. The story goes: Old lady owned since new, spec'd with brown vinyl seats, brown vinyl floor, steelies and dog dishes, and a 2.8L V6. She drove it til the engine blew up, had it towed to her mechanic, and then promptly died. Mechanic called his buddy and said I've got a one-owner, low mile Jimmy with a blown motor and a low mile (67k) TBI 350 out of an '87 Firebird Formula. Should bolt right in. Had all the accessories, including AC components, so he got it mounted in there and sold it to us. We have been pick-pick-picking away at it here and there. Got it running great, had Exhaustworks (on Fort Lowell. The good one) put in new exhaust, including cats, all the way to Flowmasters with chrome tips angled down tastefully out the back. Starts right up every time, runs strong, and needs to be finished up.$8850 out the door. Good rubber, new windshield, and such a friggin flex. Lots more pictures, thorough walk-around video, and free Carfax are available at www.tucsonfutureclassics.com. We are appointment-only so please call or text 520-268-6244 for more information or to schedule a test drive. If you aren t local Arizona, and considering buying sight unseen, let s get a dialogue going via text at that number so you can get more acquainted with the car.

CLEAN CARFAX | NON-SMOKER | ACCIDENT-FREE | LOCAL TRADE | FLORIDA CAR

This 2018 Toyota RAV4 XLE is a well-rounded and highly dependable compact SUV that continues to be one of the most trusted vehicles in its class. Known for its long-term reliability, low cost of ownership, and everyday practicality, the RAV4 remains a top choice for drivers seeking comfort, efficiency, and versatility.

Finished in Super White with a Black interior, this RAV4 offers a clean, timeless appearance that appeals to a wide range of buyers. As a local Florida trade, this vehicle has benefited from a mild climate and consistent ownership. It is a non-smoker vehicle, accident-free, and supported by a clean CARFAX, giving added confidence in its history and overall condition.

The XLE trim level provides an excellent balance of comfort and convenience while maintaining Toyotas reputation for durability. With 104,081 miles, this RAV4 reflects typical, well-distributed usage and continues to offer dependable performance suitable for daily commuting, family use, or weekend travel.

Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed with quality materials and a driver-focused layout. Features include a power-adjustable drivers seat, dual-zone automatic climate control, a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, steering wheel-mounted controls, and a backup camera. The interior is spacious and comfortable, with seating for five passengers and generous legroom in both rows. The rear seats fold flat to provide expanded cargo space, making this SUV practical for hauling gear, groceries, or luggage.

Under the hood, the 2018 RAV4 is powered by Toyotas proven 2.5L four-cylinder engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission. This powertrain delivers responsive performance while maintaining strong fuel efficiency. The Front-Wheel Drive (FWD) drivetrain helps keep operating costs low and provides confident handling for everyday driving conditions.

Safety has always been a priority for Toyota, and the RAV4 is no exception. Its solid construction, excellent visibility, and predictable road manners contribute to a confident driving experience in both city and highway environments.

Toyota RAV4 models consistently rank among the best-selling SUVs in the market due to their longevity, strong resale value, and broad appeal. If you are searching for a dependable, well-equipped, and fuel-efficient SUV with a clean history, this 2018 Toyota RAV4 XLE is an excellent option worth considering.

description:
Introducing the 2018 Chevrolet Trax LT, the perfect combination of style, performance, and practicality. This compact SUV is designed to take on any adventure, with a spacious interior and impressive features.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful Ecotec 1.4L Turbo I4 engine, delivering an impressive 138 horsepower and 148 foot-pounds of torque. Paired with a smooth 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, this Trax offers a dynamic and responsive driving experience.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a modern and comfortable interior. The LT trim level comes equipped with premium cloth seats, providing both style and comfort. The 60/40 split-folding rear seats offer versatile cargo space, making it easy to transport all your gear.

But the 2018 Trax LT is not just about functionality, it also offers a range of advanced technology features. Stay connected on the go with the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system, featuring a 7-inch touchscreen display, smartphone integration, and available navigation.

For added convenience and safety, this Trax also includes features such as a rearview camera, keyless entry, and available forward collision warning. With its 5-star overall safety rating from the NHTSA, you can have peace of mind while on the road.

So why wait? Experience the 2018 Chevrolet Trax LT for yourself and see why it's the perfect SUV for your needs. Visit our dealership today and take it for a test drive. You won't be disappointed.

Mike Molstead Motors is going the extra mile for our customers. WE WILL BRING THIS CAR TO YOU FOR A TEST DRIVE! If you elect to move forward, we can also complete your paperwork wherever you are! Delivery available Nationwide, with FREE delivery within 250 miles! This 2018 Buick Envision Essence, has a Midnight Amethyst Metallic exterior and Ebony interior color with only 108,243 miles. Stock Number 2T3526D. You can connect with us by calling 641-228-7220. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Preferred Equipment Group 1SL
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

This 2018 Ford Edge SEL blends comfort, capability, and sharp looks in one well-equipped SUV. Finished with the SEL Sport Appearance Package and 19" Premium Magnetic Metallic wheels, it stands out with front and rear Magnetic Metallic skid plates and a bold, modern stance. With 134,872 miles, this Edge has been well-driven and remains ready for the road ahead.
Inside, enjoy leather-trimmed heated bucket seats, a heated steering wheel, and automatic temperature control, all part of the Cold Weather Package—perfect for year-round comfort. The panoramic Vista Roof fills the cabin with natural light, while the SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System and premium 9-speaker audio system keep you connected and entertained.
Practical features include a rear exterior parking camera and the Class II Trailer Tow Package for added versatility. Smooth-shifting automatic transmission and Equipment Group 201A round out this feature-packed Edge, making it a great choice for daily driving or weekend adventures.

Delivery available Nationwide, with FREE delivery within 250 miles! This 2018 Ford Edge Titanium, has a Lightning Blue exterior and Ceramic interior color with only 158,298 miles.     Equipment Group 301A ($3,400 value)
      Panoramic Vista Roof ($1,595 value)
      • Includes power panoramic vista roof with one touch express open and close and power sunshade.
      Convenience
      • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
      Safety and Security
      • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
      • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
      Technology and Telematics
      • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
      • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in this 2018 Hyundai Tucson Value. This well-equipped SUV is designed to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

Boasting a powerful 1.6L I4 DGI Turbocharged engine paired with a 7-Speed Automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, the Tucson Value delivers exceptional efficiency with an EPA-estimated 24 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway. But this SUV is more than just a fuel-sipping marvel – it's also packed with a host of advanced features that prioritize your safety and convenience:

• Collision Warning System
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Lane Keeping Assist
• Backup Camera
• Voice Recognition
• Bluetooth Hands-Free

In addition to these cutting-edge technologies, the Tucson Value also comes equipped with the Cargo Package, which includes a Cargo Tray, Cargo Net, and First Aid Kit – ensuring your adventures are both organized and well-prepared.

Slip into the driver's seat and experience the refined comfort of the Tucson's interior. Heated front seats and dual-zone automatic climate control keep you and your passengers cozy, while the power driver's seat and leather-wrapped steering wheel provide a premium, personalized driving experience. The available power liftgate and panoramic sunroof add an extra touch of convenience and style.

Safety is a top priority in the Rogue S, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies that include Blind Spot Warning and Electronic Stability Control. You can drive with confidence, knowing that your vehicle is equipped to help keep you and your passengers secure.

Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure, the 2018 Nissan Rogue S is the perfect companion. Great Gas Mileage! Clean Carfax. Fully Inspected.

The 2018 Chevrolet Equinox Premier is finished in Nightfall Gray Metallic and presents a refined compact SUV profile with subtle premium detailing. Exterior features include a factory-installed trailer hitch with body-color close-out cover, dual stainless-steel exhaust with bright tips, and trailering equipment, giving the Equinox a clean, upscale appearance with added utility.

Inside, the cabin is trimmed in Gray with perforated leather-appointed seating surfaces and front bucket seats. Comfort features include 8-way power-adjustable driver and front passenger seats, heated front seats, premium color-keyed carpeted floor mats, and a well-laid-out interior designed for everyday driving and longer trips.

Technology is centered around the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with an 8-inch touchscreen display and includes Bluetooth for phone connectivity, SiriusXM satellite radio capability, multiple USB data and charging ports for front and rear passengers, and a six-speaker audio system to support media access and in-vehicle connectivity.

Power comes from the 2.0L turbocharged 4-cylinder SIDI VVT engine paired with an electronic 9-speed automatic transmission. Chassis and control features include four-wheel antilock disc brakes, a 3.17 final drive axle ratio, and a GVWR rating of 4,850 lbs, supporting confident performance and balanced road manners.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance with this exceptional 2018 INFINITI QX60 Base. This sophisticated SUV is a true masterpiece, blending cutting-edge technology, unparalleled comfort, and dynamic handling to deliver an unrivaled driving experience.

• **COMES WITH FREE 90 DAY/3,000 MILE ALLSTATE LIMITED WARRANTY**
• Deluxe Technology Package
• Premium Plus Package
• Navigation System
• Bose Cabin Surround Sound System
• 2nd & 3rd Row Moonroof with Power Rear Sunshade
• Lane Departure Warning System
• Intelligent Cruise Control
• Auto Side Dimming Mirrors
• High Beam Assist
• Motion Activated Liftgate
• Around View Monitor with Moving Object Detection
• Back-Up Collision Intervention (BCI)
• Blind Spot Intervention System (BSI)
• Blind Spot Warning System (BSW)
• Lane Departure Prevention (LDP)
• Predictive Forward Collision Warning (PFCW)
• Climate-Controlled Front Seats
• Heated 2nd-Row Seats
• Wheels: 20" 15-Spoke Aluminum-Alloy

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 engine and equipped with Intelligent All-Wheel Drive, this QX60 delivers impressive performance and confidence-inspiring handling, no matter the road conditions. The seamless Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) ensures a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the advanced safety features, including Predictive Forward Collision Warning and Blind Spot Intervention, provide added peace of mind.

Step inside and be enveloped in a world of luxury. The Bose Cabin Surround Sound System, with its 15 high-performance speakers, delivers a truly immersive audio experience. The heated and climate-controlled front seats, along with the heated second-row seats, ensure exceptional comfort for all occupants. The spacious and versatile interior, with its power-folding third-row seat, offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making this QX60 the perfect companion for your adventures.

The Deluxe Technology Package and Premium Plus Package further enhance the driving experience, with features like the Around View Monitor, Intelligent Cruise Control, and the intuitive INFINITI Navigation system. These cutting-edge technologies not only make your drive more convenient but also more engaging and enjoyable.

This 2018 INFINITI QX60 Base is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. With its exceptional performance, unparalleled luxury, and advanced safety features, it's the perfect choice for the discerning buyer who demands the very best. Visit our showroom today and experience the power, sophistication, and refinement of this remarkable SUV for yourself.

description:
One owner: this 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LT was maintained by a single careful owner and arrived at our shop in such excellent condition that technicians performed only light dealer preparation. That rare near showroom state speaks to responsible ownership and reduces immediate maintenance concerns for the next buyer. The Equinox LT pairs efficient four cylinder performance, roomy interior flexibility, and strong safety features to deliver dependable daily driving and weekend versatility.

Performance and efficiency: The Equinox LT offers responsive four cylinder power and a smooth automatic transmission tuned for comfortable acceleration and competitive fuel economy. Composed ride quality and predictable handling make this crossover ideal for commuting, family errands, and highway travel.

Exterior and utility: Clean exterior styling, alloy wheels, and practical roof rails present a modern and functional appearance. The cargo area provides generous cargo volume with split folding rear seats to adapt for luggage, sports equipment, or larger loads. Easy rear hatch access and secure tie down points improve everyday usability.

Interior comfort and features: LT trim includes upgraded cloth seating, power driver seat, and user friendly controls that enhance comfort and convenience. Ample passenger room and thoughtful storage compartments make long trips more comfortable for driver and passengers alike.

Technology and connectivity: Built in infotainment supports Bluetooth hands free calling, auxiliary and USB inputs, and smartphone audio for music and navigation apps. Clear instrument displays and an intuitive center stack keep essential information accessible and reduce distraction.

Safety and reliability: Multiple airbags, antilock brakes, stability control, and traction control contribute to occupant protection and driving confidence. Recent inspection and light dealer servicing further support short term reliability and owner peace of mind.

Condition and value: One owner and minimal shop work required make this 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LT a smart value for buyers seeking a dependable, well maintained crossover at a competitive price. Financing and service options are available to fit your needs.

Contact us today to schedule a test drive!

Discover the perfect blend of style, versatility, and capability with the 2018 Dodge Journey SE. This exceptional SUV offers a dynamic driving experience and a wealth of advanced features to elevate your everyday adventures.

• POPULAR EQUIPMENT GROUP: Includes Leather Wrapped Shift Knob, Interior Observation Mirror, Leather Wrapped Steering Wheel, Air Conditioning w/3 Zone Temp Control
• CONNECTIVITY GROUP: Includes Radio: 4.3S, Uconnect Voice Command w/Bluetooth, Leather Wrapped Shift Knob, Leather Wrapped Steering Wheel
• BLACKTOP PACKAGE: Includes Wheels: 17" x 6.5" Aluminum w/Blacktop Package, Black Headlamp Bezels, Gloss Black Grille

The Journey SE's striking black exterior exudes a bold, confident presence, while the well-appointed interior provides a comfortable and connected driving experience. With seating for up to seven passengers, this versatile SUV offers ample space for your family and friends, along with the flexibility to accommodate your cargo needs.

Powered by a 2.4L I4 DOHC 16V Dual VVT engine and a 4-Speed Automatic VLP transmission, the Journey SE delivers a smooth and efficient performance, with an impressive fuel economy of 19 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway. Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend getaway, this SUV is ready to take you there with confidence and style.

Step inside and discover the wealth of advanced technology features that elevate your driving experience. The Uconnect voice command system with Bluetooth connectivity allows you to stay connected and in control, while the 4.3" touch screen display provides easy access to your favorite music, navigation, and more. The 3-zone automatic climate control system ensures everyone on board enjoys their ideal temperature, while the leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob add a touch of refinement.

Designed with your safety in mind, the Journey SE comes equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including airbags, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control, providing you and your loved ones with the protection you deserve.

This exceptional 2018 Dodge Journey SE is now available at our dealership, waiting to become the perfect addition to your lifestyle. Schedule a test drive today and experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and capability that this SUV has to offer.

The 2018 Ford Escape SE offers a dynamic blend of versatile efficiency and compact capability, finished in a modern Ingot Silver exterior. Powered by the responsive EcoBoost 2.0L I4 turbocharged engine delivering 245 horsepower and 275 lb-ft of torque, this agile SUV provides confident, spirited performance for daily driving and weekend adventures through its smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and an intelligent all-wheel-drive system with Curve Control for enhanced stability.

The popular SE trim outfits the Escape with 17-inch painted aluminum wheels, all-season tires, and signature chrome-accented detailing. Inside, you'll find durable cloth seating surfaces with heated front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel with mounted controls, and contemporary dark brushed aluminum interior accents. The versatile and spacious cabin offers a 60/40 split-folding rear seat for flexible cargo space, along with dual-zone automatic climate control and a 6-speaker audio system with SYNC 3 connectivity.

Advanced technology features include the SYNC 3 infotainment system with a 6.5-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, and available SYNC Connect with remote vehicle access. The Escape SE also boasts the available Ford Co-Pilot360 suite of driver-assist technologies including adaptive cruise control and active noise cancellation for enhanced comfort and confidence on every journey.

Engineered for smart versatility and everyday practicality, this Escape achieves an EPA-estimated 20 MPG city/27 MPG highway while offering up to 3,500 pounds of towing capacity when properly equipped.

Experience Hassle-Free Shopping at Ames Ford Lincoln:

- Premium Quality Assurance: Rest assured with our meticulous vehicle inspections and reconditioning, averaging over $2,000 per car, ensuring your peace of mind when purchasing a pre-owned vehicle. That's why they're all backed by our 7-Day Like it or Return it Money Back Guarantee.

- Non-commissioned Sales Consultants: Means no pushy sales tactics, just friendly professionals to help you find the best car for your needs.

- Unmatched Transparency: Prior to your purchase, gain full visibility into the service history of the vehicle, ensuring complete transparency and confidence in your decision.

- Our Best Price Upfront: We recognize the extensive research done by shoppers, hence we offer highly competitive prices online to match your needs and expectations.

- Express Checkout for Time Efficiency: Streamline your purchase process by completing most of the deal remotely, whether from the comfort of your workplace or home, saving you valuable time.

The 2018 Ford Explorer XLT is a powerful and versatile SUV that delivers the space, comfort, and capability today's drivers need. With its bold exterior styling, confident stance, and smooth, composed ride, the Explorer is built to handle everything from daily commutes to family road trips with ease. Known for its strong performance and dependable engineering, this XLT trim offers a perfect balance of practicality and modern design.

Inside, the Explorer XLT features a spacious and thoughtfully designed interior with seating for up to seven passengers. Comfort and convenience come standard with premium cloth seating, a power-adjustable driver's seat, tri-zone climate control, and an intuitive infotainment system with a larger touch screen, Bluetooth connectivity, and voice commands. Flot-flat rear seating provides impressive cargo flexibility, making it easy to carry passengers, groceries, or weekend gear without compromise.

This Explorer is Ford Blue Certified, giving you added peace of mind and exceptional value. Certification includes a 90-day/4,000-mile limited warranty, 24/7 roadside assistance, and 11,000 Ford Pass rewards points that can be used toward future maintenance or service. With its strong safety features, proven reliability, and certified benefits, the 2018 Ford Explorer XLT is a smart and confident choice for anyone looking a for a well-equipped and dependable SUV.

It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you. Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe. Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. description: *Earnhardt Toyota of Mesa is pleased to offer you this Clean CARFAX 2018 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited 4x2 in Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat with a Light Frost Beige and Black interior.* With *149,486 miles*, this Grand Cherokee delivers a refined blend of comfort, capability, and upscale design that continues to make it one of the most popular midsize SUVs on the road.This Grand Cherokee Limited is powered by a smooth and capable *3.6L V6 engine* paired with an automatic transmission, providing confident acceleration and a composed driving experience for both city and highway travel. Rear-wheel drive keeps the ride balanced and efficient, with EPA-estimated fuel economy of *19 MPG city and 26 MPG highway*, making it a practical choice for daily commuting or longer trips.The *Granite Crystal Metallic* exterior gives this SUV a sophisticated, modern appearance with clean lines and a strong stance. Inside, the *Light Frost Beige and Black interior* creates a bright, upscale cabin environment with premium materials and thoughtful design throughout. Power-adjustable front seats with memory, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a spacious layout ensure comfort for both driver and passengers.Technology and convenience are well represented with an intuitive infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, USB ports, a driver information center, and a power liftgate that adds everyday practicality. The interior is quiet and refined, offering a confident, comfortable ride whether running errands or heading out on the highway.Safety and driver-assistance features include a rearview camera, rear parking sensors, blind spot monitoring, traction and stability control, and a full airbag system designed to support peace of mind behind the wheel. According to the CARFAX report, this Grand Cherokee carries a *Clean CARFAX* history, adding further confidence to its overall value.If you're looking for a well-equipped SUV with a premium feel, strong V6 performance, and timeless Jeep styling, this *2018 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited* is a compelling option.*Earnhardt Toyota of Mesa**6136 E Auto Loop Ave, Mesa, AZ 85206**480-807-9700*

To be competitive and give our customers the best possible value. We are pricing select vehicles at or below our cost. We aim to increase our volume and offer our customers the best possible experience. We are a family-owned store. Both of our owners (brothers) are based in Arizona. The store is staffed with residents, veterans, and retirees, and we all contribute to the success of our community. Our kids go to the local schools, we donate to local charities, and we volunteer throughout our communities. We would appreciate the opportunity to earn your business. We just got this sharp and very well-cared-for premium suv from a very trusted national lender. The last owner took really nice care of this Nissan. It has a fantastic 57,469 miles, that is only an average of 7,183 miles driven per year!! The very sharp and upgraded pearl white exterior paint looks great and is in excellent condition especially for its year and the miles. The equally sharp premium interior is equally nice and has been well-maintained, there is no sign it has been smoked in. This is very well equipped with all the options listed above, plus a long, long list of factory upgrades that make it a very, very nice upgraded luxury suv that looks and drives great — and the overall condition reflects how well it’s been cared for. The Carfax shows a very minor incident , there is absolutely no sign of repair. It looks great!! In addition it has just been fully serviced by our Nissan specialist, including a comprehensive multi-point pre-owned vehicle inspection, and everything checked out in excellent condition. Since this is a Carfax-certified vehicle with an excellent service history and a fully completed pre-owned inspection, it qualifies for several certified pre-owned (CPO) extended warranty options at reduced rates. Our family environment and great pricing not only make Goldie’s Motors one of the most comfortable places to buy a car, but it also makes us one of the FASTEST. You can drive out of our dealership in less than an hour after selecting your future car! WE ARE OPEN 6 DAYS A WEEK. Dressed in a sleek Brilliant Silver exterior, this 4D Sport Utility vehicle is powered by a 1.6L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, ensuring a spirited drive while maintaining impressive fuel efficiency. The Kicks SR s CVT with Xtronic transmission offers seamless gear shifts, making every journey smooth and enjoyable. Safety is paramount in the Kicks SR, featuring a suite of advanced technologies like the Blind Spot Monitor, Cross-Traffic Alert, and Front Collision Mitigation. These features, combined with integrated turn signal mirrors and a comprehensive airbag system, provide peace of mind on every drive. The vehicle s Brake Assist and Stability Control further enhance safety by ensuring optimal handling in various conditions. Inside, the Kicks SR offers a tech-savvy experience with Smart Device Integration and a Back-Up Camera, making connectivity and maneuvering effortless. The leather steering wheel and adjustable steering wheel cater to comfort, while the Remote Engine Start feature adds convenience to your daily routine. With its stylish design and robust feature set, the 2018 Nissan Kicks SR is the ideal companion for those seeking a dynamic and secure driving experience. Be sure to call or visit Camelback Hyundai Kia to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and style with this 2018 Kia Niro Plug-In Hybrid LX. Boasting a striking White exterior, this eco-friendly vehicle is not only kind to the environment but also a true head-turner on the road.

• Snow White Pearl
• Mud Guards
• Cargo Net

Packed with a range of impressive features, the Niro Plug-In Hybrid LX is designed to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the 6 Speakers, AM/FM/MP3/SiriusXM Satellite Radio, and the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. Stay comfortable with the Automatic Temperature Control and Front Dual Zone A/C, while the Power Windows and Remote Keyless Entry add to the overall ease of use.

Safety is a top priority, and the Niro Plug-In Hybrid LX delivers. With Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, you can drive with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected. The Rear View Camera and Low Tire Pressure Warning further enhance your peace of mind on the road.

Beyond the impressive features, the Niro Plug-In Hybrid LX offers exceptional value. With its 1.6L I4 engine and FWD drivetrain, this vehicle delivers a remarkable blend of efficiency and performance. The 4-Wheel Disc Brakes and Four Wheel Independent Suspension ensure a smooth and responsive ride, while the Traction Control and Speed-Sensing Steering provide added control and confidence.

Discover the perfect balance of style, technology, and efficiency with this 2018 Kia Niro Plug-In Hybrid LX. At just $12,900, this vehicle represents an outstanding opportunity to own a well-equipped, eco-friendly car at an exceptional price. Visit our showroom today and experience the Niro Plug-In Hybrid LX for yourself. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional value and the seamless ownership experience it offers.

Discover the perfect blend of style, capability, and technology in this 2018 Chevrolet Traverse 3LT. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive performance, this SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Navigation System

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, this Traverse delivers a dynamic and efficient ride. Enjoy the confidence of front-wheel drive as you navigate the roads with ease, all while achieving an impressive 18 city/27 highway mpg.

Step inside and discover a cabin that combines style and functionality. The leather-appointed seating, heated front seats, and power driver's seat ensure maximum comfort, while the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained. The 10-speaker Bose premium audio system will elevate your listening experience, while the rear air conditioning and power liftgate add to the overall convenience.

Safety is a top priority, and this Traverse is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assist technologies. From the OnStar emergency communication system to the front and side airbags, you can feel secure on every journey. The four-wheel independent suspension and electronic stability control further enhance the vehicle's handling and stability, giving you the confidence to tackle any road with ease.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating your daily commute, this 2018 Chevrolet Traverse 3LT is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, cutting-edge features, and sleek design, it's a vehicle that will exceed your expectations and make every drive a pleasure.

We invite you to experience the exceptional value and quality of this Traverse for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team guide you through a test drive. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll see why this SUV is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.
