Vehicle Details
Experience refined comfort and confident performance with this 2018 Volvo XC60 T5 Momentum, now available in Fletcher, NC. This stylish AWD SUV pairs a responsive 4-cylinder 2.0L gasoline engine with Volvo's renowned safety and engineering, delivering an engaging drive whether navigating city streets or winding mountain roads. The cabin is thoughtfully designed with premium materials and an intuitive layout, perfect for daily commuting or weekend adventures. Stay connected and entertained with Android Auto and seamless Hands Free Bluetooth integration, while the built-in Navigation system guides you to your destination with ease. Reverse parking is simple and secure thanks to the Back-Up Camera, and this Volvo XC60 comes with a CARFAX Clean Report for added peace of mind. With all the essential tech and safety features, this vehicle blends modern convenience with Volvo's long-standing commitment to protection. This 2018 Volvo XC60 T5 Momentum is competitively priced and offers the best price in the Fletcher, NC area—exceptional value for a well-maintained luxury compact SUV. AWD capability provides enhanced traction and control in variable weather conditions, making this Volvo a smart choice for drivers who demand comfort, safety, and reliability. Don't miss the chance to own a premium SUV at an unbeatable price in Fletcher, NC. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and see why this 2018 Volvo XC60 T5 Momentum stands out among pre-owned luxury SUVs.

Equipment
This 2018 Volvo XC60 T5 offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. This model offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. The leather seats in this Volvo XC60 are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path. Bluetooth technology is built into it, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This unit has auto-adjust speed for safe following. This 2018 Volvo XC60 T5 has satellite radio capabilities. The vehicle's Lane Departure Warning keeps you safe by alerting you when you drift from your lane. Keep your hands warm all winter with a heated steering wheel in this model . with XM/Sirus Satellite Radio you are no longer restricted by poor quality local radio stations while driving this 2018 Volvo XC60 T5. Anywhere on the planet, you will have hundreds of digital stations to choose from.

Packages

Hunter Auto Group has been family-owned and operated since 1940 and offers a comprehensive vehicle inspection on every pre-owned vehicle we sell. Have peace of mind with every vehicle being quality inspected and repaired by top-notch mechanics. We also offer market-based pricing on every car we sell so You never pay too much. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and versatility with this 2018 Chevrolet Trax LS. This compact crossover SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and tackle any adventure with its impressive capabilities.

Since we opened our doors on October 3rd, 1988, we've been fortunate to become one of the most successful automotive dealership groups in the state of Virginia. From our humble beginnings as a Hyundai dealership (when most Americans didn't even know what a Hyundai was) to our new Hyundai, Nissan, Volkswagen, Subaru and Prestige Collection dealerships today, we are proud to be the dealer with good people and great values for over 30 years!

• LPO, PROTECTION PACKAGE
• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio
• Premium audio system: Chevrolet MyLink
• Air Conditioning
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• ABS brakes
• Dual front impact airbags
• Dual front side impact airbags
• Rear side impact airbag
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Cloth Seat Trim

Powered by the efficient ECOTEC 1.4L I4 SMPI DOHC Turbocharged VVT engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Trax LS delivers an impressive 25 city/33 highway MPG, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures. With its spacious interior and versatile cargo area, you'll have ample room to accommodate all your needs, whether it's hauling gear, transporting passengers, or simply enjoying the ride.

The Trax LS comes equipped with a host of advanced features that elevate your driving experience. The Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with a 7-inch color touchscreen provides seamless connectivity, allowing you to access your favorite music, navigation, and more with ease. The available OnStar and Chevrolet connected services keep you connected and secure, while the rear-view camera and available rear parking sensors ensure you can navigate tight spaces with confidence.

Safety is a top priority, and the Trax LS delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control work together to protect you and your passengers in the event of an accident.

This 2018 Chevrolet Trax LS is the perfect blend of style, technology, and versatility. With its impressive efficiency, spacious interior, and advanced safety features, it's the ideal choice for those seeking a compact crossover that can handle any adventure. Visit our showroom today to experience the Trax LS for yourself and discover why it's the perfect addition to your lifestyle.

The Southern Team Internet Market Value Price (iMVP) is set by the Virginia market, not by us, so you get a fair, low price right up front! With iMVP, First Team uses a third-party source, Kelley Blue Book's Fair Market Value to automatically set our prices – so you're assured of getting a great price that's never misleading, with no hassles, no surprises. Our Used Vehicle prices include our Platinum Protection Package, at no additional charge including:
1. Nitrogen Filled Tires
2. Theft Recovery Assist
3. Two years of Lojack Connected Car

description: Bright, roomy, and ready for wherever life takes you — this 2018 Dodge Durango SXT is a great blend of family-friendly space and V6 performance. Powered by the smooth Pentastar 3.6L V6 (293 hp / 260 lb-ft) paired to an 8-speed automatic, it delivers confident acceleration for highway runs and everyday driving while offering the utility you need for passengers, gear, or weekend towing. Factory-equipped for comfort, convenience and safety, this Durango SXT includes: - Pentastar 3.6L V6 engine with an efficient, refined 8-speed automatic transmission for responsive, composed performance. - Uconnect infotainment system with a crisp touchscreen and built-in smartphone integration (Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatible) so you can stream, navigate and call hands-free. - Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming, USB and auxiliary inputs for charging and media. - Spacious three-row seating that accommodates up to seven passengers with versatile seat-folding for plenty of cargo room when you need it. - Comfortable cloth seating surfaces, with driver-friendly adjustments and easy-to-reach controls. - Multi-zone climate control to keep front and rear passengers comfortable on every drive. - Rearview camera for confident backing and parking visibility. - Steering wheel-mounted audio and cruise controls for convenience and safety. - Remote keyless entry, power windows, power door locks and power-adjustable mirrors for everyday ease. - A comprehensive safety suite with multiple airbags, ABS, traction and electronic stability control to help keep you and your passengers protected. This particular Durango is in excellent overall condition and comes with a clean CARFAX — a reassuring history to go with a thoroughly enjoyable driving experience. Cheerful, capable and practical, this Durango SXT is ready to be your next dependable family hauler or weekend adventure vehicle. 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LS for Sale in Manassas Park, VA | Practical SUV with Efficiency, Technology, and Everyday ComfortThe 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LS is a versatile and fuel-efficient compact SUV designed to handle daily driving with ease and comfort. Equipped with a 1.5L DOHC engine and a 6-speed automatic transmission, this front-wheel-drive Equinox delivers a smooth ride, solid fuel economy, and dependable performance. With a comfortable interior and modern connectivity features, it s a great option for commuting, family use, or weekend trips. Key FeaturesEngine & Performance
  • Efficient 1.5L DOHC 4-cylinder engine offering reliable performance and good fuel economy.
  • 6-speed automatic transmission with overdrive for smooth and responsive shifting.
  • Front-wheel drive (FWD) paired with traction control and electronic stability control for confident handling.
  • Independent suspension and speed-sensing steering enhance ride comfort and control.
Interior Comfort
  • Comfortable Medium Ash Gray cloth interior with supportive front bucket seats.
  • Air conditioning and rear window defroster provide year-round comfort.
  • Split-folding rear seats allow for flexible cargo and passenger space.
Technology & Audio
  • Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with a clear, user-friendly interface.
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility for seamless smartphone integration.
  • Bluetooth connectivity, USB port, and steering-wheel-mounted audio controls for convenience.
Safety Features
  • Comprehensive airbag system including front, side, and overhead airbags.
  • 4-wheel ABS brakes, brake assist, and electronic stability control for enhanced safety.
  • Rear-view camera and rear park assist help with parking and maneuvering.
  • OnStar and Chevrolet connected services capability add peace of mind on the road.
Exterior Features
  • Clean Summit White exterior with body-colored bumpers and subtle styling accents.
  • 17-inch aluminum wheels and rear spoiler add both function and style.
  • Automatic headlights and power mirrors improve visibility and everyday convenience.
Why Choose the 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LS?The 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LS offers a balanced combination of efficiency, practicality, and modern technology. With its comfortable interior, smart safety features, and user-friendly infotainment system, this SUV is a great choice for drivers seeking a dependable and versatile vehicle for everyday use.Schedule Your Test Drive Today!

Great Service HistoryHoliday-ready. Trail-proven. Family approved.There s something timeless about a Jeep in the winter. This 2018 Jeep Cherokee Trailhawk brings the holiday spirit home for the holidays. It s the version built for snow-dusted backroads, last-minute gift runs, and weekend escapes without asking luxury-SUV money.At just $11,989, this Trailhawk undercuts comparable listings by over $4,500, while delivering the most capable Cherokee trim Jeep makes. The Trailhawk isn t a badge it s a promise. Jeep engineered this trim to go where others hesitate, making it ideal for winter roads, mountain trips, and everyday reliability.SafetyBecause getting everyone home matters most.Highlights:
  • Blind Spot Monitoring with Rear Cross-Path Detection
  • Electronic Stability Control & Roll Mitigation
  • Multiple airbags throughout the cabin
  • Hill Descent Control for steep or slick terrain
  • Rearview camera for tight winter parking
Holiday travel means full cabins and busy roads. The Trailhawk answers with solid safety engineering and modern driver assistance quietly working in the background while you focus on the moment.FeaturesBuilt tough, dressed comfortably.Highlights:

  • Remote start because cold mornings are real

This Trailhawk blends rugged capability with the kind of interior comfort families actually use warm, intuitive, and durable enough for boots, bags, and winter gear.2-Owner | Great Service History

description:
Introducing the sleek and stylish 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LT! Built to impress with its modern design and advanced features, this mid-size SUV is the perfect blend of form and function. Boasting a spacious interior and a smooth ride, the Equinox LT is the ultimate vehicle for both daily commutes and weekend adventures.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful yet efficient 1.5L turbo engine, delivering an impressive 170 horsepower. Paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, you'll experience a smooth and responsive driving experience. Plus, with a fuel economy of up to 32 MPG on the highway, the Equinox LT will save you money at the pump.

Step inside the Equinox LT and you'll be greeted with a spacious and comfortable cabin. With seating for up to five passengers and ample cargo space, this SUV is perfect for families, friends, and everything in between. The LT trim comes equipped with premium cloth seats and a 7-inch touchscreen display with Chevrolet MyLink, providing seamless connectivity to your favorite apps and music.

But that's not all, the Equinox LT also includes advanced safety features such as lane departure warning, forward collision alert, and a rearview camera. You can drive with confidence knowing that you and your passengers are protected on the road.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to drive home in the 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LT. With its stunning design, powerful performance, and advanced features, this SUV is the complete package. Visit your local Chevrolet dealership today to experience the Equinox LT for yourself.

description:
Ask for a free Carfax Report! Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and versatility with this 2018 Chevrolet Trax LT, now available at Tom Hodges Mitsubishi under stock number H8108. This compact SUV, with its sleek Mosaic Black Metallic exterior and sophisticated Jet Black/Light Ash Gray interior, is ready to elevate your daily drives and weekend adventures.

Powered by an efficient ECOTEC Turbo 1.4L engine with Variable Valve Timing, this Trax delivers a responsive 138 horsepower and 148 lb-ft of torque, ensuring a peppy performance while maintaining excellent fuel economy. The 6-speed automatic transmission provides smooth shifts, making your city commutes and highway cruises equally enjoyable.

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior featuring deluxe cloth/leatherette seat trim that combines comfort and durability. The driver's seat offers 4-way manual adjustment with power lumbar support, while the front passenger enjoys a 2-way manual adjustable seat with a convenient flat-folding seatback for added versatility.

Tech-savvy drivers will appreciate the Chevrolet MyLink Radio with a 7" diagonal color touch-screen, complete with Android Auto and Apple CarPlay compatibility. Stay connected on the go with the Chevrolet 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, offering internet access for up to 7 devices. The six-speaker audio system, along with SiriusXM Satellite Radio, ensures your favorite tunes always sound crisp and clear.

Safety is paramount in the 2018 Trax LT, featuring 10 airbags, including frontal, knee, side-impact, and roof rail protection. The StabiliTrak stability control system with Traction Control helps you maintain confidence in various driving conditions. A Rear Vision Camera assists with parking and maneuvering in tight spaces.

Additional features that set this Trax apart include a remote vehicle starter system, power windows with Express-Up/Down for the driver, cruise control, and a theft-deterrent system. The LT Convenience Package adds extra comfort and functionality to your driving experience.

With its compact size and all-wheel-drive chassis, this Trax is perfect for navigating busy city streets while still offering the capability to tackle light off-road adventures. The roof-mounted luggage rack provides extra storage options for your gear, making this the ideal companion for weekend getaways.

Despite its 97,988 miles, this Trax boasts a clean CARFAX report, indicating it has been well-maintained throughout its life. Don't miss this opportunity to own a versatile, feature-packed SUV that combines Chevrolet's renowned reliability with modern comfort and technology. Visit Tom Hodges Mitsubishi today and experience the 2018 Chevrolet Trax LT for yourself! Discover the perfect blend of style, capability, and convenience with this 2018 Ford EcoSport S. This compact crossover SUV is the ideal companion for your on-the-go lifestyle, offering a dynamic driving experience and a wealth of premium features.

Highlighted by its sleek Gray exterior, the EcoSport S boasts an impressive array of amenities, including:

• Moonroof/Sunroof
• Leather Interior
• Navigation/GPS
• Bluetooth Equipped
• SL Option Pkg
• Heated Seats
• Adaptive Cruise Control

Under the hood, the EcoSport S is powered by a 2.0L I4 Ti-VCT GDI engine, paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission and 4WD capabilities. This efficient powertrain delivers an exceptional balance of performance and fuel economy, with an EPA-estimated 23 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway.

The EcoSport's interior is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, featuring a SYNC Communications & Entertainment System, Air Conditioning, and a host of advanced safety technologies, including Dual Front Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and an Exterior Parking Camera Rear.

This vehicle has been carefully inspected and certified, ensuring you can drive with confidence. With just 66,038 miles on the odometer, this EcoSport S is ready to provide years of reliable service.

description:
Experience the Unparalleled Capability of the 2018 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport S

This rugged and versatile 2018 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport S is the perfect companion for your next adventure. With its powerful 3.6L V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and legendary 4-wheel drive system, this Wrangler is ready to tackle any terrain with confidence.

• Quick Order Package 24S Sport S
• Dual Top Group
• Technology Group
• Cold Weather Group
• Convenience Group

These premium features elevate your driving experience, providing the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of remote keyless entry, automatic headlamps, and power-heated mirrors, while staying connected with the Uconnect 4 infotainment system featuring a 7-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto.

When the weather turns cold, the heated steering wheel and front seats will keep you cozy, while the dual-top configuration allows you to choose between the premium black soft top or the sturdy three-piece hard top. The Mopar all-weather floor mats ensure your Wrangler stays clean and protected, no matter the conditions.

This Wrangler's sleek black exterior and rugged off-road tires give it a bold, adventurous look that's sure to turn heads. With its impressive 18 city/23 highway MPG, you can explore the great outdoors without sacrificing fuel efficiency.

Whether you're tackling the trails or navigating the daily commute, this 2018 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport S is the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style. Experience the freedom and excitement of Jeep ownership today.

description:
2018 Honda HR-V LX Versatile Design, Dependable PerformanceThe 2018 Honda HR-V LX is a practical and stylish subcompact crossover that blends urban maneuverability with the versatility of an SUV. Ideal for commuters, small families, or anyone needing a compact yet spacious vehicle, the HR-V LX offers the signature Honda reliability and intelligent packaging. From its fuel-efficient engine to its flexible interior layout, the HR-V LX delivers a comfortable and functional driving experience tailored to daily life.Designed with a sleek profile and surprisingly roomy interior, the HR-V LX offers a smart balance of agility, fuel economy, and practicality making it an ideal companion for city streets and weekend adventures alike.Performance
  • 1.8L i-VTEC Inline-4 Engine
    Produces 141 horsepower and 127 lb-ft of torque, delivering dependable everyday power with impressive fuel efficiency.
  • Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT)
    Ensures smooth and efficient acceleration with minimal maintenance.
  • Front-Wheel Drive (FWD)
    Provides confident handling and a lighter weight for improved fuel economy.
  • Eco Assist System
    Helps promote efficient driving habits and optimizes fuel usage.
  • Fuel Economy
    EPA-estimated 28 mpg city/34 mpg highway, making it one of the most efficient in its class.
Interior
  • 5-Passenger Seating with Premium Cloth Upholstery
    Offers a comfortable and clean layout, with supportive front seats and generous legroom for rear passengers.
  • 2nd-Row Magic Seat
    Features a highly flexible folding mechanism that allows for tall, long, or utility-mode cargo configurations.
  • 5-Inch Color LCD Display
    Equipped with Bluetooth HandsFreeLink and streaming audio capability.
  • Air Conditioning with Air-Filtration System
    Maintains cabin comfort in all conditions.
  • 60/40 Split Rear Seatbacks
    Easily fold down to create up to 58.8 cubic feet of cargo space.
Dimensions
  • Overall Length: 169.1 inches
  • Width: 69.8 inches
  • Height: 63.2 inches
  • Wheelbase: 102.8 inches
  • Curb Weight: Approx. 2,884 lbs
  • Cargo Volume:
    • Behind Rear Seats: 24.3 cu. ft.
    • With Rear Seats Folded: 58.8 cu. ft.
Compact in size but surprisingly roomy inside, the HR-V offers more flexibility than many larger crossovers.Safety
  • Multi-Angle Rearview Camera
    Provides Normal, Top-Down, and Wide views when reversing for greater visibility and safety.
  • Vehicle Stability Assist (VSA ) with Traction Control
    Enhances handling during adverse conditions and sharp turns.
  • Anti-Lock Braking System (ABS) with Brake Assist
    Increases control during emergency stops.
  • Advanced Compatibility Engineering (ACE ) Body Structure
    Improves occupant protection and crash performance.
  • Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS)
    Alerts the driver to underinflated tires to ensure proper vehicle operation and safety.
Highlights? Efficient 1.8L i-VTEC engine with excellent fuel economy
? Magic Seat system offers multiple cargo configurations
? Multi-angle rearview camera for enhanced visibility
? Smooth CVT transmission for seamless city and highway driving
? Flexible and spacious interior with fold-flat rear seats
? Compact footprint perfect for urban environments
? Bluetooth connectivity and a user-friendly infotainment layout
? Honda s trusted safety and reliabilitySummaryThe 2018 Honda HR-V LX delivers exceptional value for drivers seeking a compact crossover that s big on utility and efficiency. With its clever Magic Seat system, fuel-saving engineering, and smart safety technologies, the HR-V LX stands out as a leader in its segment. Whether navigating busy streets or packing up for a weekend trip, this vehicle is built to keep pace with modern lifestyles while maintaining Honda's reputation for long-term reliability and comfort.

description:
Sophisticated, comfortable, and impressively well-equipped, this 2018 Nissan Murano SV is the perfect crossover for families, commuters, and anyone who wants luxury-like comfort and style in every drive. Powered by a smooth and dependable 3.5L V6 engine, the Murano delivers 260 horsepower and excellent fuel efficiency, with a refined Xtronic CVT® transmission providing responsive acceleration and confident passing power.

Key features include:
• BLUETOOTH
• Rearview Camera
• Navigation System
• 11 Speakers
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Heated Front Seats
• Leather-Appointed Seat Trim
• Power Driver's Seat with Lumbar Support
• Blind Spot Warning
• Rear Cross Traffic Alert
• Automatic Emergency Braking

The Murano's exterior stands out with Nissan's bold V-Motion grille, sharp LED signature accents, floating-roof design, and sleek aerodynamic body lines, giving it a premium look that punches far above its price point. Inside, the spacious cabin is designed for long trips and daily driving, with NASA-inspired Zero Gravity Seats delivering exceptional comfort.

Advanced technology is a major highlight, offering NissanConnect® with an 8-inch color touchscreen, Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto™, and a suite of driver-assist features that provide peace of mind on every trip. With its upscale interior, smooth V6 power, and standout styling, the 2018 Nissan Murano SV offers luxury-like comfort and capability at an exceptional value.

This Murano SV is a certified pre-owned vehicle, having undergone a rigorous 167-point inspection and reconditioning process to ensure it meets Nissan's high standards. It comes with a comprehensive warranty and 24/7 roadside assistance, providing you with the confidence and peace of mind you deserve.

If you're searching for a Nissan Murano in the Newport News or Hampton Roads area, don't wait - visit Southern Mazda Newport News today or schedule your test drive to experience the comfort, performance, and sophistication of this 2018 Murano SV. With its exceptional features and value, it's the perfect crossover to elevate your driving experience.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and versatility in this 2018 Nissan Rogue S. With its sleek gray exterior and well-appointed interior, this Rogue is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• No accidents or damage reported to CARFAX
• Chrome Rear Bumper Protector
• Blind Spot Warning
• Brake Assist
• Electronic Stability Control
• Speed Control
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Under the hood, the 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine, paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, delivers an impressive 26 city/33 highway MPG, ensuring you can go further on every tank. The Rogue's spacious cabin and flexible cargo area make it the ideal companion for your everyday adventures, whether it's a weekend getaway or a trip to the home improvement store.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a host of advanced features, including a premium audio system, dual-zone climate control, and a user-friendly infotainment system with smartphone integration. The Rogue's safety suite, including Blind Spot Warning and Brake Assist, provides added peace of mind on the road.

But the Rogue's true strength lies in its versatility. The 60/40 split-folding rear seats and generous cargo space allow you to easily adapt to your changing needs, whether you're hauling oversized items or packing for a family vacation. And with the available all-wheel-drive system, you can conquer any terrain with confidence.

This 2018 Nissan Rogue S is a true standout in its class, offering the perfect blend of style, technology, and capability. With its impressive fuel efficiency, spacious interior, and advanced safety features, it's the ideal choice for the modern driver who demands more from their vehicle.

Don't miss your chance to experience the Rogue's exceptional value and performance. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this Nissan Rogue S is the perfect fit for your lifestyle. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional quality and the unbeatable customer service you'll receive from our team.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and versatility with this 2018 Ford Escape S. This compact SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and adapt to your every need.

• SERVICE RECORD AVAILABLE
• GOOD BRAKES
• GOOD TIRES
• BLUE TOOTH HANDS FREE
• WHEELS: 17" SPARKLE SILVER-PAINTED ALUMINUM
• Equipment Group 100A

Powered by a 2.5L i-VCT engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Escape delivers an impressive 21 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. With its front-wheel-drive configuration, you'll enjoy confident handling and responsive steering, ensuring a smooth and enjoyable ride.

Beyond the impressive performance, this Escape is equipped with a wealth of features that cater to your comfort and convenience. The SYNC Communications & Entertainment System keeps you connected, while the air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry provide the modern amenities you expect. Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and electronic stability control to give you peace of mind on the road.

Boasting a stylish exterior in a striking Blue hue, this 2018 Ford Escape S is a head-turner that will turn heads wherever you go. The 17-inch alloy wheels and body-color bumpers add a touch of refinement, while the rear window wiper and variably intermittent wipers ensure clear visibility in any weather.

Step inside and experience the spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring cloth front bucket seats, a front center armrest, and a split-folding rear seat that offers versatile cargo-carrying capabilities. The telescoping steering wheel and tilt function allow you to find your perfect driving position, while the illuminated entry and driver's vanity mirror add an extra level of convenience.

Don't miss your chance to make this 2018 Ford Escape S your own. With its impressive combination of performance, features, and style, this compact SUV is a must-see. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this Escape can elevate your driving experience.

description: Experience refined style, agile performance, and everyday versatility with this 2018 Audi Q3 Sport Premium. Designed to deliver the signature Audi driving experience in a compact luxury SUV, the Q3 is an excellent choice for drivers who want premium comfort and confident handling in a manageable, city-friendly size.Powered by a responsive turbocharged engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission, the Q3 Sport Premium offers energetic acceleration and impressive efficiency. Its balanced ride and precise steering provide a composed, enjoyable drive whether you're navigating local roads or cruising on the highway.Inside, the cabin reflects Audi's attention to detail and commitment to quality. Premium materials, a clean and modern layout, and a driver-focused design create an upscale environment that feels both comfortable and intuitive. Advanced technology enhances every drive with an easy-to-use infotainment system, clear digital displays, and convenient connectivity features that keep you informed and entertained. Driver-assistance technologies add an extra layer of confidence and peace of mind.The Audi Q3 also delivers impressive practicality, with a flexible interior and ample cargo space that adapts easily to daily errands, commuting, or weekend travel. Its compact footprint makes it easy to maneuver and park, while still offering the versatility expected from an SUV.With its sleek design, engaging performance, and renowned Audi craftsmanship, the 2018 Audi Q3 Sport Premium stands out as a luxury compact SUV that delivers comfort, capability, and style. Come see us at Volkswagen of Fallston, 2110 Bel Air Rd, Fallston, MD 21047. Just minutes away!

Vehicle Details
The 2018 Subaru Crosstrek Limited offers a perfect balance of capability, comfort, and everyday practicality—built for Montana roads and for drivers who want confidence in any season. Finished in Crystal Black Silica, this Crosstrek pairs rugged styling with an upscale, refined presence.

With Subaru’s trusted AWD system and a 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, the Crosstrek delivers stable, sure-footed performance whether you're navigating Bozeman winters, heading up to Bridger, or cruising through town. The 7-speed CVT keeps the drive smooth, efficient, and easy.

Inside, the Limited trim elevates the experience with leather seating, clean design, and a comfortable cabin engineered for both short commutes and long weekend escapes. The four-door layout and smart cargo space make it an excellent fit for busy lifestyles, outdoor gear, and everyday errands alike.

For drivers seeking reliability, versatility, and the elevated feel of a Limited model, this Crosstrek stands out as a well-rounded small SUV. See it today at Snyder Motors Inc. in Bozeman.

Equipment
This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. The leather seats in it are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. Protect this 2018 Subaru Crosstrek from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. This small suv features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. Apple CarPlay: Seamless smartphone integration for this model - stay connected and entertained on the go! The Subaru Crosstrek offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. This model offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this unit is easy with the climate control system. It has a 4 Cyl, 2.0L high output engine. This unit is painted with a sleek and sophisticated black color. This vehicle is equipped with all wheel drive.

description:
Built to dominate the road is easily seen in our 2023 Ford F-150 Raptor R SuperCrew 4X4 with the Sunroof & Tailgate Pack in Agate Black Metallic! Motivated by a SuperCharged 5.2 Liter High Output V8 providing 700hp to a 10 Speed SelectShift Automatic transmission geared for going off the grid. Multiple off-road modes, Trail Control, and a long-travel suspension with Fox Racing Shox let you leave the pavement far behind, and this Four Wheel Drive truck scores nearly 18mpg on the highway. Built for the bold, our F-150 boasts LED lighting, performance bumpers, functional air extractors, heavy-duty skid plates, aluminum running boards, flared fenders, Custom Method wheels, 38X13.50R17 Nitto Trail Grappler M/T Tires, a Custom Front Bumper, and our pack's dual-pane sunroof and power tailgate.

A comfortable and commanding layout greets you in our Raptor cabin with heated/ventilated leather power front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable pedals, keyless access/ignition, and remote start. Connections come easy with a 12-inch driver display, a 12-inch touchscreen, WiFi compatibility, voice control, Android Auto/Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, and B&O Unleashed audio.

Keep moving confidently, knowing Ford's smart approach to safety includes a 360-degree camera system, adaptive cruise control, automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, lane-keeping assistance, and Pro Trailer Backup Assist. Now find out for yourself why our F-150 Raptor is so popular! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Nashville Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

Introducing the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor R - a true off-road beast that's ready to conquer any terrain. With its uncompromising performance and unparalleled capabilities, this exceptional truck is the ultimate expression of Ford's engineering prowess.

Prepare to be blown away by this Raptor R's impressive list of custom features:

• Whipple Gen 6 3.8L Upgraded Supercharger
• 975 Horsepower on 93 octane
• Paint Matched Bumpers and Fender Flares
• Method Wheels w/37'' Toyo Tires
• Spray In Liner
• Tinted Windows
• Hard Folding Bed Cover

But the Raptor R's capabilities go far beyond mere customization. This vehicle is packed with the latest and greatest technology, including:

• SYNC 4 with Enhanced Voice Recognition
• 14-Speaker B&O Unleashed Sound System
• Heads-Up Display
• 360-Degree Camera System
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Seats
• Twin Panel Moonroof

Elevating the Raptor R's performance is the EQUIPMENT GROUP 803A, which includes a host of impressive upgrades:

• Raptor R Unique Grille and Hood Vent
• Modular Front Bumper
• Upgraded Dual Exhaust
• Raptor R Exterior Graphics and Badging
• Dual Valve Shocks
• Raptor R-Specific 17-inch Forged Aluminum Wheels

This truck is more than just a statement of power, it's a testament to Ford's commitment to innovation and excellence. With its uncompromising off-road capabilities, advanced technology, and unparalleled style, the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor R is the ultimate choice for the discerning driver who demands the best.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel of this extraordinary vehicle, conquering the most challenging terrain with ease and confidence. The Raptor R's 975 horsepower and advanced suspension system will ensure that every drive is an unforgettable experience, whether you're tackling the wilderness or navigating the city streets.

Don't settle for anything less than the best. Experience the true power and capability of the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor R. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the thrill of owning this remarkable truck.

description:
Introducing the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor R, a true off-road champion that's ready to conquer any terrain. With its powerful 5.2L supercharged V8 engine, 10-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive, this Raptor R is engineered to deliver unparalleled performance and capability.

This stunning Raptor R comes equipped with a wealth of premium features, including:

• Local Trade, Non-Smoker
• Equipment Group 803A Raptor R
• Tough Bed Spray-In Bedliner
• Modular Front Bumper
• Upgraded Dual Exhaust
• Raptor R Exterior Graphics, Grille, and Hood Vent
• Interior Code Orange Raptor R Badging
• Unique Carbon Fiber Appliques
• RECARO Front Seats with Code Orange Stitching
• 17" Forged Aluminum Wheels

But the Raptor R's capabilities extend far beyond its impressive list of features. This truck is built to dominate the off-road, with its dual valve shocks, 37-inch all-terrain tires, and bead-lock capable wheels. Whether you're tackling rugged trails or navigating the daily commute, the Raptor R delivers a thrilling driving experience.

Inside, the Raptor R pampers you with a wealth of premium amenities, including a 14-speaker B&O Unleashed sound system, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a heads-up display. The SYNC 4 infotainment system with enhanced voice recognition keeps you connected and in control.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like lane departure warning, automatic high-beam headlights, and an emergency communication system. The Raptor R's advanced safety technologies provide you and your passengers with the confidence to tackle any adventure.

With its uncompromising performance, premium features, and bold styling, the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor R is the ultimate off-road machine. This Lifted 2026 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali Ultimate Crew Cab 4X4 Dually includes a 3-inch Coginto Suspension Lift with Fabricated Upper Control Arms and Four Wheel Alignment, 20-inch American Force Shrapnel Gloss Black Wheels, 37X13.50R24 Toyo Open Country R/T Trail Tires, Chrome Delete Custom Blackout Grille, Side Mirror Caps, Side Emblems, Window Trim, Door Handles, Step Trim, Front & Rear Emblems, Color Match Fender Flares, Professionally Installed Window Tint w/Lifetime Warranty. Installed by our Certified Lift Tech: Rand! *Modifications are optional and are not included in the advertised price.*

Diesel powered, our One Owner 2026 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali Ultimate Crew Cab 4X4 Dually with the Gooseneck/5th Wheel Package rewards you with rugged capability for the long haul in Onyx Black! Motivated by a TurboCharged 6.6 Liter DuraMax Diesel V8 delivering 470hp and 975lb-ft of torque to a 10 Speed Allison Automatic transmission. This Four Wheel Drive truck also masters the miles with an off-road suspension, Digital Variable Steering, and a dominating design. Exterior highlights include the Gooseneck/5th Wheel Pack's stamped bed holes with caps, a 7-pin trailer harness, power sunroof, power-assist steps, LED lighting, a 3-inch Coginto Suspension Lift with Fabricated Upper Control Arms and Four Wheel Alignment, 20-inch American Force Shrapnel Gloss Black Wheels, 37X13.50R24 Toyo Open Country R/T Trail Tires, Chrome Delete Custom Blackout Grille, Side Mirror Caps, Side Emblems, Window Trim, Door Handles, Step Trim, Front & Rear Emblems, Color Match Fender Flares, Professionally Installed Window Tint w/Lifetime Warranty, a spray-on bedliner, and a MultiPro tailgate with a built-in Kicker sound system.

Our Denali Ultimate offers top-shelf amenities, including heated/ventilated leather power front seats, heated rear seats, a heated leather steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, a power sliding rear window, and sophisticated technologies. Enjoy crisp Bose Performance audio, backed by a 13.4-inch touchscreen, a 12.3-inch driver display, Google Built-in, wireless phone connectivity, WiFi compatibility, and wireless charging.

Intelligent GMC safety measures let you drive confidently, protected by features such as adaptive cruise control, automatic braking, a head-up display, HD Surround Vision, a digital rearview mirror, trailer blind-spot monitoring, Pro Grade Trailering equipment, and more. With all that, our Sierra 3500 Denali Ultimate won't complain when the big jobs call! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Oklahoma City Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

description: This 2026 Ford F-450 Super Duty Platinum Crew Cab is the ultimate statement of luxury, power, and road presence, made even more impressive with an odometer thats 1,708 miles below the market average. Finished in stunning Glacier Gray Metallic Tri-Coat and offered as a one-owner vehicle with a clean Carfax, this F-450 delivers unmatched capability paired with high-end comfort and aggressive custom styling.Under the hood is Fords legendary 6.7L High Output Power Stroke Turbo Diesel V8, producing an astonishing 500 horsepower and 1,200 lb-ft of torque, making this one of the most powerful pickup trucks ever built. This engine delivers effortless towing, brutal low-end torque, and dominant highway performance in any situation. Paired with 4WD, a 4.30 limited-slip rear axle, and the FX4 Off-Road Package, this truck is engineered for extreme hauling, heavy trailers, and off-road confidence. While heavy-duty trucks are not EPA rated, real-world owners typically report 1418 MPG on the highway, which is exceptional for a dually of this size and capability.Inside, the Platinum trim offers true flagship-level luxury. Youll enjoy exclusive Platinum leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, memory driver seat and pedals, panoramic sunroof, heads-up display, built-in navigation, and the incredible B&O Unleashed Sound System by Bang & Olufsen that delivers premium, concert-quality audio. Technology is top-tier with the Ford Connectivity Package including 5G modem, SiriusXM 360L, Pro Power Onboard 2kW, and a fully digital cockpit designed for modern connectivity and convenience.Safety and driver-assist features include blind spot monitoring, electronic stability control, hill descent control, auto high-beam headlights, flow-through center console, and advanced braking and stability systems that provide confidence whether youre towing or cruising.What truly separates this F-450 from anything else on the road are its high-end aftermarket upgrades. This truck features a professionally installed 3-inch lift kit, massive 24-inch Arena wheels, and aggressive 37-inch mud terrain tires, giving it a dominating stance, increased ground clearance, and an unmatched visual presence. These upgrades dramatically enhance both off-road capability and street appeal, making this truck as bold as it is capable.With dual rear wheels, the 14,000 lb GVWR payload package, off-road tuned shock absorbers, and factory FX4 enhancements, this F-450 is built for extreme workloads while still delivering first-class luxury and ride quality.Most importantly, this F-450 has been fully inspected, runs and drives like new, and represents a rare opportunity to own a nearly new Platinum diesel with ultra-low miles and premium custom upgrades. Finding a truck with this combination of condition, power, luxury, and aftermarket build is extremely rare.This vehicle is available now at Covert Ford of Hutto. Visit our showroom today and experience the Compass Sport for yourself. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional quality and unbeatable value.

Safety is also a top priority in the Equinox LT, with features like a rearview camera, lane departure warning, and automatic emergency braking to keep you and your passengers safe.

Don't miss out on this fantastic vehicle and drive into the future with the 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LT.

description:
Introducing the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX, a true powerhouse that commands the road with unparalleled performance and style. This exceptional vehicle is more than just a truck - it's a statement of pure automotive excellence.

• Diamond Black Crystal Pearlcoat exterior with Black interior
• Quick Order Package 29Y
• Navigation System

Engineered to thrill, the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX boasts a 6.2L Supercharged HEMI V8 SRT engine that delivers an adrenaline-fueled driving experience. With 8-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, this truck is ready to conquer any terrain with ease. Brace yourself for an unmatched 10 city/14 highway MPG rating, a testament to its power and capability.

Beyond its impressive performance, the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX is packed with cutting-edge features that elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Uconnect 5 Nav system with a 12-inch display, providing seamless connectivity and navigation. The adaptive suspension ensures a smooth and responsive ride, while the 10-speaker audio system delivers a concert-hall-like experience.

Safety is paramount, and the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX delivers with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera to the Electronic Stability Control, you can navigate with confidence and peace of mind.

Slip behind the wheel of the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX, and you'll be captivated by the bold, aggressive styling that commands attention on the road. The Black exterior mirrors, with their heating elements and supplemental turn signals, add a touch of refinement, while the 18-inch Black Paint/Polish Aluminum wheels exude a rugged, yet sophisticated, presence.

Indulge in the luxurious comfort of the Cloth/Vinyl Bucket Seats, complete with power 4-way driver lumbar adjustment and a front center armrest with storage. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob provide a premium feel, while the tilt and telescoping functionality ensures a personalized driving position.

Experience the unparalleled power, style, and technology of the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX. This exceptional vehicle is more than just a truck - it's a statement of your unwavering commitment to performance and innovation. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the 2023 Ram 1500 TRX is the ultimate choice for the discerning driver.

description:
Discover the ultimate in power, capability, and luxury with this 2023 Ford F-450SD Platinum DRW. This exceptional heavy-duty pickup is built to conquer any task, whether you're towing a heavy load, navigating off-road terrain, or seeking unparalleled comfort on the road.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this F-450SD Platinum DRW is the epitome of versatility and refinement. Highlights include:

• Collision Avoidance System
• Collision Warning System
• Active Parking Assist
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Leather Seats
• Heated and Cooled Seats
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Lane Keeping Assist
• Navigation System
• Adaptive Headlights
• Touchscreen Controls
• Heads-Up Display
• Backup Camera
• Keyless Access with Push Button Start

Under the hood, the powerful 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged Power Stroke engine delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, while the 10-speed automatic transmission ensures smooth, responsive power delivery. The FX4 Off-Road Package further enhances the vehicle's capabilities, with features like Hill Descent Control, off-road-tuned shock absorbers, and skid plates.

Elevating the driving experience, this F-450SD Platinum DRW boasts a host of premium amenities, including a twin-panel power moonroof, Max Recline Seats, and a Snow Plow Prep Package. The advanced SYNC 4 system with Enhanced Voice Recognition and the B&O Unleashed Sound System by Bang & Olufsen provide seamless connectivity and exceptional audio quality.

Safety and convenience are also top priorities, with features like the Heads-Up Display, Rear Camera, and Blind-Spot Monitors ensuring a confident and secure driving experience. Plus, with a GVWR of 14,000 lbs, this truck is ready to handle your toughest jobs with ease.

Whether you're tackling demanding worksite duties, embarking on off-road adventures, or simply seeking a luxurious and capable daily driver, this 2023 Ford F-450SD Platinum DRW is the perfect choice. description:
Our One Owner, Diesel powered 2023 Ford F-250 Platinum Crew Cab 4X4 in Carbonized Gray Metallic is a luxe truck! Featuring a TurboCharged 6.7 Liter PowerStroke Diesel V8 supplying 475hp and 1050lb-ft of torque to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission. The handy onboard generator is a remarkable resource at work or play, and this Four Wheel Drive truck is also a top-notch towing machine. Impressive and aggressive, our F-250 has a Custom Wicked Lift, Custom KG1 wheels, Custom Light Bar, Custom Fusion Bumpers, LED lighting, power running boards, a panoramic sunroof, PowerScope trailer mirrors, and a power tailgate.

World-class accommodations await in our Platinum cabin, featuring heated/ventilated leather power front seats, heated rear seats, a heated leather power steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable pedals, remote start, and a power-sliding rear window. Turn up the B&O audio system for your favorite soundtrack and turn to the 12-inch driver display, a 12-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, connected navigation, WiFi compatibility, Bluetooth, voice recognition, and wireless charging for superior connectivity.

Ford supports safer trucking with a head-up display, adaptive cruise control, front/rear automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, intersection assistance, a 360-degree camera system, parking sensors, lane-keeping assistance, and more. Built Ford tough, our F-250 Platinum is a better way to get things done! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Hurst Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

description: Get ready to dominate every road, worksite, and trail with the 2026 Chevy Silverado 2500HD LTZ the ultimate heavy-duty pickup that blends brute strength, advanced capability, and upscale refinement like never before. Under the hood sits the mighty 6.6-liter Duramax Turbo-Diesel V8, engineered to deliver impressive torque and hauling muscle that can conquer your toughest jobs. With class-leading towing and diesel torque on demand, this Silverado makes hauling large trailers, heavy equipment, or weekend toys feel effortless every time. Performance Capability Rugged 6.6-liter Duramax Turbo-Diesel V8, paired with an Allison 10-speed automatic transmission for smooth shifts under load. Best-in-class towing potential and stout torque delivery for maximum hauling confidence. Full-time 4-wheel drive and advanced off-road traction systems built to perform in mud, snow, or steep grades. Premium LTZ Comfort, Tech Style Step inside and youre greeted by a well-appointed cabin that elevates the experience beyond typical heavy-duty work trucks: Jet Black leather-appointed seats with power adjustments and comfort features for long hauls. Integrated Apple CarPlay and Android Auto with advanced touchscreen infotainment. Adaptive cruise control, forward collision warning, and modern driver-assistance systems for peace of mind on every drive. Smart Capability From trailering cameras and in-vehicle trailering apps to heavy-duty towing packages and diesel exhaust braking, this LTZ is designed for both maximum performance and effortless control. Bold Exterior Presence Command attention on the road with signature LED lighting, chrome accents, rugged alloy wheels, and a confident stance that reflects serious capability without sacrificing style. In short: the 2026 Silverado 2500HD LTZ 6.6 Turbo Diesel 4WD is not just a pickup its a workhorse with premium soul, ready for big jobs, epic trips, and everyday driving with class and confidence.

Introducing the sleek and powerful 2015 Tesla Model S 85D! This luxurious electric vehicle offers the ultimate driving experience with its innovative technology and stunning design.

Equipped with dual motors and all-wheel drive, the 85D can accelerate from 0 to 60 mph in just 3.1 seconds, making it one of the fastest production cars on the market. But don't let its speed fool you, the 85D also offers a smooth and quiet ride with its advanced suspension and noise-cancelling technology.

Step inside the spacious and modern interior and you'll be greeted with premium features such as a 17-inch touchscreen display, panoramic sunroof, and heated seats. Enjoy the convenience of keyless entry and start, as well as the safety of a rearview camera and autopilot capabilities.

But the true beauty of the 85D lies in its environmentally-friendly nature. With a range of over 250 miles per charge and zero emissions, you can feel good about driving this car while also saving on gas costs.

Don't miss your chance to own this cutting-edge 2015 Tesla Model S 85D. With only [number] miles on the odometer, it's practically brand new and waiting for you to take it for a spin. Schedule a test drive today and experience the future of driving.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2025 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali Ultimate Technology Package. This powerful and versatile pickup is designed to handle any challenge with uncompromising capability and refined luxury.

• 3" Lift
• Aftermarket Wheels & Tires
• Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package
• Upfitter Switch Kit (5)
• Preferred Equipment Group 5SB
• Technology Package

Beneath the bold, commanding presence of the Sierra 3500HD lies a true workhorse. The Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine, paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission, delivers exceptional power and efficiency, ensuring you can tackle any task with ease. The 4WD system provides confident control in even the most demanding conditions, making this truck a reliable companion for your toughest jobs.

The Denali Ultimate Technology Package elevates the driving experience with a host of premium features. The stunning Onyx Black exterior with the Vader Chrome Signature Denali Ultimate Grille creates a striking, head-turning appearance. Inside, the cabin is adorned with genuine wood accents, full-grain leather seating, and a 13.4" diagonal GMC Premium Information Display, seamlessly integrating technology and luxury.

Convenience and connectivity are at the forefront, with features like Wireless Charging, Wireless Phone Projection, and a Bose Premium Series 12-Speaker System. The Heads-Up Display, Trailer Camera Provisions, and In-Vehicle Trailering App make towing and hauling a breeze, while the Ultrasonic Front & Rear Park Assist and Rear Cross Traffic Alert provide added peace of mind.

Safety is also a top priority, with advanced driver-assistance technologies like Forward Collision Alert, Automatic Emergency Braking, and Lane Departure Warning System. The Trailer Tire Pressure Monitor Sensors and ProGrade Trailering System further enhance your confidence behind the wheel, no matter the task at hand.

Experience the unparalleled capability, technology, and refinement of the 2025 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali Ultimate. This exceptional truck is ready to elevate your driving experience and tackle your toughest challenges. Visit our showroom today to explore this remarkable vehicle and discover how it can transform the way you work and play.

This Lifted 2025 Ford F-250 Platinum Crew Cab 4X4 includes a 5-inch BDS Stage 2 Radius Arm Lift Kit w/Fox 2.5 Elite Series Remote Resi Front & Rear Shocks and Four Wheel Alignment, 24-inch American Force Forged "Provoke" Full Gloss Black Wheels, 37X13.50R24 Nitto Ridge Grappler Tires. Installed by our Certified Lift Tech: Richard! *Modifications are optional and are not included in the advertised price.*

Our One Owner, No Accidents Reported, Diesel-powered 2025 Ford F-250 Platinum Crew Cab 4X4 with the FX4 Off-Road Package puts you in command of bold capability in Ruby Red! Motivated by a TurboCharged 6.7 Liter PowerStroke Diesel V8 supplying 475hp and 1050lb-ft of torque to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission for mighty strength. Features like a Pro Power Onboard generator, built-in payload/trailer-tongue scales, a power tailgate, power running boards, LED lighting, skid plates, power twin-panel sunroof, spray-on Bedliner, a 5-inch BDS Stage 2 Radius Arm Lift Kit w/Fox 2.5 Elite Series Remote Resi Front & Rear Shocks and Four Wheel Alignment, 24-inch American Force Forged "Provoke" Full Gloss Black Wheels, 37X13.50R24 Nitto Ridge Grappler Tires, and PowerScope mirrors help our Four Wheel Drive F-250 look good and work strong.

Our Platinum cabin helps you stay comfortable with heated/ventilated leather power front and heated rear seats, a heated leather power steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable pedals, and a power sliding rear window. Digitally dominate the daily grind with a 12-inch touchscreen, a 12-inch productivity screen, connected navigation, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, wireless charging, WiFi compatibility, Bluetooth, voice control, and B&O Unleashed audio by Bang & Olufsen.

For safer trucking, Ford delivers a head-up display, Pro Trailer backup/hitch assistance, front/rear automatic braking, trailer blind-spot monitoring, a 360-degree camera system, lane-keeping assistance, a tailgate-down camera, parking sensors, and more. Ready for a workout, our F-250 Platinum is a better way to go! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Garland Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. description:
Elevate Your Driving Experience with the Exceptional 2025 Ram 3500 Limited

Introducing the 2025 Ram 3500 Limited, a true powerhouse that redefines the boundaries of capability and luxury. Meticulously crafted to exceed your every expectation, this remarkable vehicle is the embodiment of uncompromising performance and refined sophistication.

Key features of this exceptional Ram 3500 Limited include:
• 6.7L I-6 Diesel Turbocharged (Cummins) engine
• Limited Level 1 Equipment Group with advanced driver-assistance technologies
• Max Tow Package for exceptional towing capacity
• Night Edition for a bold, commanding presence
• Power Sunroof for an open-air driving experience

Stepping inside, you'll be captivated by the unparalleled level of craftsmanship and attention to detail. The cabin is adorned with genuine wood accents, premium leather seating, and a state-of-the-art Uconnect 5 infotainment system with a 14.4-inch display. The Limited's advanced features, such as the Surround View Camera System, Adaptive Steering System, and Drowsy Driver Detection, work in harmony to provide a driving experience that is both effortless and secure.

For those who demand the utmost in capability, the 2025 Ram 3500 Limited delivers. The Max Tow Package, which includes an Auto Level Rear Air Suspension and 5th Wheel/Gooseneck Towing Prep Group, allows you to confidently handle the most demanding towing tasks. With a Gross Vehicle Weight Rating (GVWR) of 14,000 lbs, this powerhouse is ready to take on any challenge you put before it.

Elevating the driving experience even further, the Night Edition package adds a bold, commanding presence with its black exterior badging, body-color grille surround, and sport performance hood. The 17-inch polished aluminum wheels with dual rear wheels complete the striking look, ensuring that this Ram 3500 Limited stands out from the crowd.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or seeking a luxurious daily driver, the 2025 Ram 3500 Limited is the perfect choice. With its uncompromising performance, advanced technology, and premium appointments, this exceptional vehicle is poised to exceed your every expectation. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Experience the pinnacle of power and sophistication with this 2025 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali. This exceptional heavy-duty truck is a true workhorse, designed to tackle the toughest jobs with uncompromising capability and refined style.

Boasting a host of premium features, this Sierra 3500HD Denali is the ultimate expression of GMC's commitment to excellence. Highlights include:

• ONE OWNER, CLEAN CARFAX, and RECENT TRADE-IN
• DURAMAX 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine with 10-speed automatic transmission and 4WD
• NAVIGATION GPS, MOONROOF/SUNROOF, BLUETOOTH, and BACKUP CAMERA
• BLIND SPOT AND CROSS PATH DETECTION, POWER RUNNING BOARDS, and SNOW PLOW PREP
• DENALI RESERVE PACKAGE with TECHNOLOGY PACKAGE and HD SURROUND VISION
• REMAINDER OF FACTORY WARRANTY and LOW MILES

The powerful Duramax diesel engine delivers an impressive 470 horsepower and 975 lb-ft of torque, providing the muscle you need to conquer any challenge. Paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission and robust 4WD system, this Sierra 3500HD Denali is ready to take on the toughest terrain and heaviest loads with ease.

Inside, the Denali's premium cabin offers unparalleled comfort and convenience. The leather-wrapped, heated steering wheel, heated and ventilated front seats, and dual-zone automatic climate control ensure a relaxing driving experience, no matter the conditions. The advanced infotainment system with navigation, premium Bose audio, and wireless charging keep you connected and entertained.

Safety and technology are also top priorities, with features like the HD Surround Vision camera system, Blind Spot and Cross Traffic Alert, and a large, customizable head-up display. The Denali Reserve Package further enhances the experience with additional luxury and convenience features.

With its exceptional capabilities, premium amenities, and striking good looks, this 2025 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali is the ultimate choice for those who demand the best. Experience the power and refinement of this exceptional heavy-duty truck for yourself. Visit our showroom today to take a closer look and schedule a test drive.

Whether you're tackling rugged off-road terrain or navigating the daily commute, the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor is the ultimate companion. With its robust construction, advanced technology, and exceptional capabilities, this truck is ready to take on any challenge you throw its way.

Experience the power and versatility of the 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can transform your driving experience.

description:
This Lifted 2025 GMC Sierra 2500HD AT4 Crew Cab 4X4 includes a 4-inch CST Stage 10 Non Torsion Bar Drop Lift Kit w/Fabricated CST Upper Control Arms, CST 2.5 Adjustable Remote Resi Front & Rear Shocks and Four Wheel Alignment, 22-inch Arena Wheel Co.A109 Hustle Satin Black w/Gloss Black Ring Wheels, 37X12.50R22 Nitto Ridge Grappler Tires, Custom Paint to Entire Grille, Bumper Inserts, Hood Insert, Mirrors, Fender Flares, Bed Inserts, Rear Bumper Inserts & All Emblems, Cusotm Smoked Mirror Lights, Tail Lights, Fender Flare Lights and Roof Lights. Installed by our Certified Lift Tech: Daniel C! *Modifications are optional and are not included in the advertised price.*

Our Diesel-powered 2025 GMC Sierra 2500HD AT4 Crew Cab 4X4 with the Premium Plus Package will grab your attention in Thunderstorm Gray! Motivated by a TurboCharged 6.6 Liter DuraMax Diesel V8 providing 470hp and 975lb-ft of torque to a 10 Speed Allison Automatic transmission. This Four Wheel Drive truck also has an off-road suspension, skid plates, hill-descent control, and an Autotrac 2-speed transfer case for getting to hard-to-reach jobs. Our Sierra boasts LED lighting, red recovery hooks, a 4-inch CST Stage 10 Non Torsion Bar Drop Lift Kit w/Fabricated CST Upper Control Arms, CST 2.5 Adjustable Remote Resi Front & Rear Shocks and Four Wheel Alignment, 22-inch Arena Wheel Co.A109 Hustle Satin Black w/Gloss Black Ring Wheels, 37X12.50R22 Nitto Ridge Grappler Tires, Custom Paint to Entire Grille, Bumper Inserts, Hood Insert, Mirrors, Fender Flares, Bed Inserts, Rear Bumper Inserts & All Emblems, Cusotm Smoked Mirror Lights, Tail Lights, Fender Flare Lights and Roof Lights, a spray-on bedliner, power-sliding rear window, LED smoked amber roof marker lamps, a power sunroof, and a MultiPro tailgate for high-visibility styling.

Our AT4 cabin is your mobile command post for doing more. It features heated/ventilated leather power front seats and heated rear seats, a heated-wrapped steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, keyless access/ignition, remote start, and remarkable technologies. Highlights include a Bose audio system, a 12.3-inch driver display, a 13.4-inch touchscreen, Google Built-in, WiFi compatibility, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Bluetooth, and wireless charging.

GMC helps you stay safe as you work hard with a surround-view system, 15-inch head-up display, a bed-view camera, trailer-capable blind-spot monitoring, automatic braking, parking sensors, lane-departure warning, trailer-sway control, hill-start assistance, and more. When tough jobs call, our Sierra 2500 AT4 is ready to answer! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

Take on heavy-duty jobs, towing, hauling, and long adventures with confidence in this 2025 GMC Sierra 2500HD Denali , a premium full-size pickup built for strength, comfort, and advanced capability. With its powerful diesel heart and upscale features, this truck is ready to work hard and ride in style. This Sierra 2500HD Denali is equipped with the 6.6-liter Duramax Turbo-Diesel V8 engine paired with a 10-speed Allison automatic transmission , producing around 470 horsepower and a massive 975 lb-ft of torque for serious pulling power. The diesel torque makes it especially capable for towing trailers, boats, and heavy equipment with confidence. Inside, the Denali trim offers a refined and spacious cabin with premium leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, advanced infotainment with a large touchscreen and smartphone integration, and a host of driver-assist technologies . The upscale interior and thoughtful amenities make long days on the road more enjoyable. One of the Sierras standout capabilities is its towing potentialdepending on configuration and equipment, it can handle heavy trailers with ease, backed by advanced trailering technologies and available camera views that make hitching and maneuvering simpler. With its potent Duramax diesel V8, premium Denali comforts, and serious towing and hauling capability, this 2025 GMC Sierra 2500HD Denali 6.6L Turbo Diesel V8 is built to deliver confidence, strength, and sophistication on every drive. Schedule your test drive today and experience the power and refinement for yourself.

description: This 2025 Summit White GMC Sierra EV Denali Max Range AWD with a sleek Black interior is packed with awesome features like a 7-speaker Bose sound system, a dual-level charge cord, a heads-up display, and premium GMC infotainment. Stay extra comfy with heated and ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, and a heated steering wheel. It’s loaded with tech like adaptive suspension, auto high-beam headlights, a navigation system, and an emergency communication system via OnStar. Plus, it is equipped with a ton of safety and convenience features like dual-zone A/C, rain-sensing wipers, multiple airbags, and an auto-leveling suspension. You’ll love the spacious cabin with features like memory seats, a trip computer, and a sporty steering wheel with mounted controls. Ready for adventure with its four-wheel independent suspension and all the premium bells and whistles!

Discover the ultimate workhorse in our showroom - the 2024 Ford F-450SD Lariat DRW. This heavy-duty pickup is built to conquer any task, from hauling heavy loads to towing your biggest toys with ease.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this F-450SD is equipped to handle your toughest jobs with uncompromising capability. Highlights include:

• Wireless Charging Pad

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium materials and the latest in-vehicle technology. The Head-Up Display, 4-Way Adjustable Headrests, and Retractable Bed Side-Step add to the overall comfort and convenience.

Whether you're a contractor, a weekend warrior, or simply need a capable and reliable truck, the 2024 Ford F-450SD Lariat DRW is the perfect choice. The Denali is built with upscale comfort in mind: authentic open-pore wood and patterned aluminum trim, forge-perforated leather seats, heated and ventilated front seats, a large 13.4-inch center touchscreen paired with a 12.3-inch digital driver display, and features like the ProGrade Trailering System, HD surround vision, and adaptive cruise control with trailering. With a maximum GCWR approaching 30,000 lbs, conventional towing up to 20,000 lbs, generous payload, and the option for long bed or crew cab configuration, the 2024 Sierra 2500 Denali delivers premium strength you can feel—inside and out.

Driver-assist items such as Lane Departure Warning and Cross-Traffic Alert add crucial protection for highway and parking lot situations, enhancing confidence behind the wheel. The vehicle comes with a CARFAX Clean Report, reflecting a well-documented history and added peace of mind.

Whether you need a powerful truck for towing, hauling, or a comfortable daily driver with premium amenities, this GMC Sierra 2500 Denali checks all the boxes. With low mileage and competitive pricing in Mukwonago, WI, this truck represents strong value for clients seeking performance and luxury. Elevate your driving experience with this remarkable 2024 Ford F-350SD Platinum DRW. Boasting a powerful 6.7L High Output Power Stroke V8 Diesel engine and 4WD capabilities, this truck is ready to tackle any challenge with uncompromising performance and capability.

Standout features include:
• Bluetooth Hands Free
• Backup Camera
• 4x4
• 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged (Power Stroke)
• Twin Panel Power Moonroof
• Tough Bed Spray-In Bedliner
• 5th Wheel/Gooseneck Hitch Prep Package
• Limited Slip w/4.10 Axle Ratio
• Max Recline Seats
• Rapid-Heat Supplemental Cab Heater
• Engine Block Heater
• Front Wheel Well Liners (Pre-Installed)

This F-350SD Platinum DRW is more than just a workhorse, it's a true luxury pickup that combines power, technology, and comfort. The SYNC 4 with Enhanced Voice Recognition and the premium B&O Unleashed Sound System by Bang & Olufsen will keep you connected and entertained on every journey. With features like heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a panoramic moonroof, this truck is designed to provide the ultimate driving experience.

Towing and hauling capabilities are enhanced by the 5th Wheel/Gooseneck Hitch Prep Package, allowing you to confidently tackle even the most demanding jobs. The Tough Bed Spray-In Bedliner and the durable dual rear wheels ensure your cargo remains secure and protected.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a 360-Degree Camera System providing added peace of mind on the road. The advanced safety technologies in this F-350SD Platinum DRW are designed to keep you and your passengers safe, no matter the conditions.

This exceptional vehicle is now available at a PRICE DROP, making it an even more compelling choice for those seeking a premium, capable, and well-equipped truck. Don't miss your opportunity to experience the power, comfort, and technology of the 2024 Ford F-350SD Platinum DRW. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable truck can elevate your driving experience.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
