description:
Discover the ultimate in power, capability, and style with the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD ZR2. This exceptional heavy-duty truck is a true workhorse, built to conquer any challenge you face. Boasting a commanding presence with its bold, rugged design, the Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is ready to take on the toughest jobs with uncompromising performance.

Highlighted features of this remarkable vehicle include:

• Local Trade
• Non-Smoker
• 6.6L V8 Diesel Turbocharged (Duramax) (B20-Diesel Compatible) (470 hp [350.5 kW] @ 2800 rpm, 975 lb-ft of torque [1322 Nm] @ 1600 rpm)
• Power-Retractable Black Assist Steps with LED Lighting
• Technology Package with Rear Camera Mirror and Multicolor 15" Diagonal Head-Up Display
• Power Sunroof
• Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 3LT
• Up-Level Rear Seat with Storage Package
• ZR2 Suspension Package
• BOSE Premium 7-Speaker Sound System
• Wireless Charging
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Seats

This Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is engineered to conquer the toughest terrain and handle the most demanding jobs with ease. The powerful Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine delivers an impressive 470 horsepower and an astounding 975 lb-ft of torque, providing the muscle you need to tow, haul, and tackle any task. The advanced 10-speed automatic transmission and sophisticated 4WD system ensure seamless power delivery and exceptional control, no matter the conditions.

Beyond its impressive performance, the Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is packed with premium features that elevate the driving experience. The Technology Package, with its Rear Camera Mirror and Head-Up Display, keeps you informed and connected, while the BOSE premium audio system delivers a truly immersive listening experience. Heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and heated rear seats ensure maximum comfort, even in the harshest weather.

This Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is more than just a work truck – it's a true off-road champion. The ZR2 Suspension Package, with its specialized shocks and increased ground clearance, allows you to conquer the toughest terrain with confidence. The Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package further enhances the Silverado's towing capabilities, making it the perfect companion for your most demanding adventures.

Experience the unparalleled power, capability, and refinement of the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD ZR2. This exceptional vehicle is ready to take on any challenge and elevate your driving experience to new heights. Visit our showroom today to see this impressive truck in person and discover how it can transform the way you work and play.

Our One Owner, Diesel-powered 2022 Ford F-250 Platinum Crew Cab 4X4 with the FX4 Off-Road Pack puts premium strength at your command in Star White! Motivated by a TurboCharged 6.7 Liter PowerStroke Diesel V8 that generates 475hp and 1,050lb-ft of torque for a 10 Speed Automatic transmission. This Four Wheel Drive truck also includes our trail-friendly package, with hill-descent control, off-road shocks, and robust skid plates for rugged terrain. Bold and stylish, our Ford F-250 features an exclusive FX4 graphic, Satin Aluminum accents, LED lighting, fog lamps, power running boards, a spray-on bedliner, a sunroof, Lifted with Black 20-inch Method alloy wheels, 37X12.50R20 Nitto Ridge Grapplers, and a remote-release tailgate with a built-in step.

Check out our Platinum cabin, which is as comfortable as it is capable. Black Onyx leather heated/ventilated power front and heated rear seats, a heated leather steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, remote start, and power-adjustable pedals are only a few of the upscale highlights. There's impressive technology, too, including an 8-inch productivity screen, an 8-inch touchscreen, connected navigation, Android Auto, Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, WiFi compatibility, wireless charging, and Bang & Olufsen audio.

Ford supports Super Duty safety with intelligent Co-Pilot360 systems, including a backup camera, blind-spot monitor, automatic braking, forward-collision warning, reverse parking sensors, adaptive cruise control, and more. Tough challenges need a tough truck like our F-250 Platinum! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. Our Diesel powered 2022 Ford F-250 Platinum Crew Cab 4X4 with the FX4 Off-Road Pack puts premium strength at your command in Star White! Motivated by a TurboCharged 6.7 Liter PowerStroke Diesel V8 that generates 475hp and 1,050lb-ft of torque for a 10 Speed Automatic transmission. This Four Wheel Drive truck also includes our trail-friendly package, with hill-descent control, off-road shocks, and robust skid plates for rugged terrain. Bold and stylish, our Ford F-250 features an exclusive FX4 graphic, sunroof, matching accents, LED lighting, fog lamps, power running boards, spray-on Bedliner, Custom Lift with American Force wheels, 37X13.50R24 Toyo Open Country M/T Tires, and a remote-release tailgate with a built-in step.

Check out our Platinum cabin, which is as comfortable as it is capable. Black Onyx leather heated/ventilated power front and heated rear seats, a heated leather steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, remote start, and power-adjustable pedals are only a few of the upscale highlights. There's impressive technology, too, including an 8-inch productivity screen, an 8-inch touchscreen, connected navigation, Android Auto, Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, WiFi compatibility, wireless charging, and Bang & Olufsen audio.

Ford supports Super Duty safety with intelligent Co-Pilot360 systems, including a backup camera, blind-spot monitor, automatic braking, forward-collision warning, reverse parking sensors, adaptive cruise control, and more. Tough challenges need a tough truck like our F-250 Platinum! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Hurst Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

Our Diesel-powered 2022 Ford F-250 Lariat Crew Cab 4X4 with the Ultimate Package shows off remarkable strength in Gray. Motivated by a TurboCharged 6.7 Liter PowerStroke Diesel V8 offering 475hp and 1,050lb-ft of torque to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission for amazing capability. This Four Wheel Drive truck also inspires you to take on your biggest jobs, and it catches your attention with classic Super Duty good looks. A mighty grille sets the tone, complemented by fog lamps, leveled with Custom Fuel alloy wheels, Ford's PowerScope trailer mirrors, running boards, a sunroof, and our package, which includes LED box lighting and a power-release tailgate with an access step.

A comfortable command post for getting things done, our Lariat cabin has a lot to like. Highlights include our package's leather heated/ventilated power front seats, heated rear seats, a leather-wrapped power steering wheel, power-adjustable pedals, full-color navigation, ambient lighting, keyless access, pushbutton ignition, remote start, and wireless charging. Our F-250's fantastic SYNC technology keeps you connected with an 8-inch touchscreen, Android Auto, Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, WiFi compatibility, and Bang & Olufsen audio.

Stay safe on the road with intelligent Ford Co-Pilot360 features, including a backup camera, blind-spot monitor, automatic braking, forward-collision warning, reverse parking sensors, and more. Tough challenges need a tough truck like our F-250 Lariat! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Nashville Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

Experience refined performance and confident handling with this 2016 Chrysler 300C AWD, featuring a robust 3.6L V6 gasoline engine. This well-maintained sedan blends power and comfort, delivering a smooth ride whether navigating city streets or cruising the interstate. The AWD system provides enhanced traction and stability in varied road conditions, making it a smart choice for drivers who value control and peace of mind.

Inside, the Chrysler 300C is equipped with modern conveniences to keep you connected and comfortable. Hands-free Bluetooth and XM Radio provide entertainment and seamless phone integration, while the navigation system helps you reach your destination with ease. A heated steering wheel ensures warmth and comfort during colder months, and the back-up camera improves safety and visibility when parking or maneuvering.

This Chrysler 300C combines upscale features with practical performance, offering spacious seating and a thoughtful interior layout. The exterior presents a timeless design that stands out without being flashy. Located in Paducah, KY, this vehicle is priced to sell — offering the best price in the area for comparable models. Whether you're seeking a reliable daily driver or a capable weekend tourer, this 2016 Chrysler 300C AWD delivers value, comfort, and performance. Schedule a test drive in Paducah today and experience why this is the smart buy in its class.

This 2024 White Frost Tricoat GMC Sierra 1500 Denali 4WD is well equipped and includes these features and benefits:The 2024 GMC Sierra 1500 Denali with the Reserve Package and 6.2L V8 offers premium luxury, advanced tech like a 15" HUD & Rear Camera Mirror, powerful performance with dynamic fuel management, and enhanced utility with MultiPro Power Steps & 22" Wheels, providing superior comfort, safety, and capability for both work and lifestyle, with the White Frost Tricoat paint adding a distinctive look.
Key Features & Benefits
Denali Reserve Package ($4,565)
Rear Camera Mirror: Offers an unobstructed, wide view of the rear, great for towing or large cargo.
15" Diagonal Head-Up Display (HUD): Projects critical info (speed, nav) onto the windshield, keeping eyes on the road.
Power Sunroof: Adds open-air feel and natural light.
GMC MultiPro Power Steps: Automatic, power-deployable steps for easy entry/exit, especially with lifted trucks.
22" Painted Aluminum Wheels: Larger, stylish wheels for a commanding presence and improved handling.
Engine & Performance ($2,295)
6.2L EcoTec3 V8 w/Dynamic Fuel Management: Delivers significant power (420 hp/460 lb-ft torque) for towing & acceleration, while DFM saves fuel by shutting down cylinders when not needed.
Exterior & Styling
White Frost Tricoat ($1,095): A premium, multi-layered paint finish for a sophisticated look.
Body Color Wheel Arch Moldings ($750): Seamlessly integrates wheel well flares for a cleaner, monochromatic look.
Other Denali & Reserve Perks
Luxurious Interior: Perforated leather, wood trim, heated/ventilated seats, Bose audio.
Advanced Tech: Super Cruise (hands-free driving), HD Surround Vision, large touchscreens, Wi-Fi.
Utility: MultiPro Tailgate (6 functions), available Kicker Audio System in tailgate, power bedliner.
Overall Benefits
Unmatched Comfort & Style: Top-tier Denali trim with premium materials and distinctive looks.
Superior Capability: Powerful V8, 4WD, and towing tech (Hitch View, Trailer Side Blind Zone Alert).
Cutting-Edge Technology: HUD, Rear Camera Mirror, Super Cruise (if equipped) enhance safety and convenience.
Enhanced Access & Versatility: Power steps and MultiPro tailgate simplify truck use


At Octane GMC we look forward to helping you revolutionize your entire car-shopping experience. Let our team of automotive experts answer all your questions and work with you toward getting the vehicle and the finance plan of your dreams.

This exceptional vehicle is designed to conquer any terrain, offering unparalleled capability and refined luxury. Meticulously equipped with a host of premium features, the Sierra 2500HD AT4 is the perfect companion for your adventures. Highlights include: Adaptive Cruise Control Apple CarPlay/Android Auto Backup Camera Bluetooth, Hands-Free Blind Spot Monitor Heated Steering Wheel Memory Seat Leather Seats Heated Seats Ventilated / AC Seats Push Button Start Lane Departure Warning Off Road Package Bose Audio Sunroof / Moonroof The AT4 Premium Plus Package takes this truck to the next level, adding a power sunroof, advanced technology, and high-clearance steps for uncompromised off-road capability. The Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package ensures seamless towing, while the Hitch Package provides a comprehensive towing solution. Powered by a robust 6.6L V8 engine mated to a 10-speed automatic transmission, the Sierra 2500HD AT4 delivers exceptional performance and efficiency. Whether you're tackling challenging terrain or hauling heavy loads, this truck is up to the task. Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a premium cabin that exudes comfort and sophistication. Perforated leather-appointed seats, heated and ventilated front seats, and a Bose premium audio system create an unrivaled driving experience. The advanced technology suite, including a 15-inch Head-Up Display and Wireless Charging, keeps you connected and in control. Safety is paramount in the Sierra 2500HD AT4, with features like Adaptive Cruise Control, Forward Collision Alert, and Automatic Emergency Braking providing added peace of mind on the road. Elevate your driving experience with the 2024 GMC Sierra 2500HD AT4. This exceptional truck is ready to take on any challenge, while delivering the refined luxury and advanced technology you deserve. Visit our showroom today to witness its capabilities firsthand and explore how it can transform your driving adventures.

We want you to be happy long after you've left our store, so we include a *complimentary WalserCare warranty* with most used vehicles. Every used vehicle also undergoes a *comprehensive 190-point inspection* and includes a *free CarFax History Report*. Experience the pinnacle of power and capability with the 2024 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali. This exceptional heavy-duty pickup is engineered to conquer any challenge, whether you're tackling tough job sites, towing heavy loads, or navigating rugged terrain.

Boasting a remarkable array of features, this Sierra 3500HD Denali is designed to exceed your expectations. Key highlights include:
• Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 5SA
• Snow Plow Prep/Camper Package
• Technology Package
• X31 Off-Road Package

Under the hood, the powerful Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine delivers an impressive 470 horsepower and an astounding 975 lb-ft of torque, ensuring you have the muscle to handle even the most demanding tasks. Paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission and a robust 4WD system, this Sierra 3500HD Denali is ready to take on any challenge with confidence.

Stepping inside, you'll be surrounded by premium amenities that elevate the driving experience. The Denali-exclusive interior features plush, perforated leather-appointed seats with heating and ventilation, a stunning Multicolor 15" Diagonal Head-Up Display, and a premium Bose sound system to keep you entertained on the road.

The Sierra 3500HD Denali also boasts an impressive array of advanced safety and technology features, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Automatic Emergency Braking, and the Bed View Camera with Trailer Camera Provisions, ensuring you stay connected and protected on every journey.

This exceptional vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is now available for your consideration. With low mileage and a comprehensive suite of premium features, the 2024 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali is the ultimate heavy-duty pickup that will elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Experience the unparalleled power, capability, and luxury of the 2024 GMC Sierra 3500HD Denali. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this remarkable vehicle can transform the way you work and play.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD ZR2. This exceptional truck is designed to conquer any terrain, offering unparalleled capability and premium features that will exceed your expectations.

Equipped with a powerful 6.6L V8 engine and a robust 10-speed automatic transmission, this Silverado 2500HD ZR2 delivers exceptional performance and towing capacity. Boasting a sophisticated 4WD system, you'll have the confidence to tackle any challenge, whether it's navigating rugged off-road conditions or hauling heavy loads with ease.

This vehicle comes loaded with a comprehensive suite of advanced features, including:

• Collision Warning System
• Heated Seats
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Touchscreen Controls
• Backup Camera
• Keyless Access with Push Button Start
• Apple CarPlay
• Android Auto

The Silverado 2500HD ZR2 also offers a range of premium packages that enhance its capabilities and convenience. The Technology Package, for instance, includes features like Rear Camera Mirror, Multicolor Head-Up Display, and Adaptive Cruise Control. The Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package and Snow Plow Prep/Camper Package further expand the truck's versatility, making it the perfect companion for your towing, hauling, and outdoor adventures.

Elevating the driving experience even further, this Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is equipped with a host of advanced safety and connectivity features. Enjoy the convenience of Wireless Charging, Wi-Fi Hotspot Capability, and the intuitive Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium System with SiriusXM 360L. The Rear Camera Mirror, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and In-Vehicle Trailering App System provide added confidence and control, ensuring a seamless and secure driving experience.

Step inside the cabin and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring premium leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and a heated steering wheel. The Multicolor Head-Up Display and Rear Camera Mirror further enhance your situational awareness, while the Bose Premium Audio System delivers an immersive listening experience.

With its striking Blue exterior and rugged good looks, the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is a true head-turner. But beyond its impressive appearance, this truck is built to perform, offering a winning combination of power, capability, and advanced technology that will elevate your driving experience to new heights.

If you're in the market for a capable, versatile, and well-equipped truck, the 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD ZR2 is a must-see. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can transform the way you tackle your daily tasks and weekend adventures.

description:
Rugged capability meets refined luxury in this 2024 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X 4WD, a premium off-road pickup engineered for drivers who demand strength, technology, and comfort in one bold package. Finished in striking Thunderstorm Gray, this AT4X features an aggressive stance and purpose-built design thats ready for trails, towing, and everyday driving alike.

Power comes from the advanced 3.0L I6 engine, delivering impressive torque, efficiency, and smooth performance. Paired with a responsive 10-speed automatic transmission and 4WD, this Sierra provides confident control on rough terrain, highways, and in challenging weather conditions.

Inside the spacious 4D Crew Cab, the upscale Obsidian Rush interior surrounds you with premium materials and a driver-focused layout. The Preferred Equipment Group 4SG adds high-end comfort and cutting-edge technology, while the integrated Navigation System keeps every journey on track. When its time to haul or tow, the Trailering Package provides the capability and confidence you expect from a Sierra.

Key Features Include:

3.0L I6 Engine

4WD with 10-Speed Automatic Transmission

AT4X Off-Road Performance Package

Preferred Equipment Group 4SG

Navigation System

Trailering Package

Spacious Crew Cab with Obsidian Rush Interior

With 40,761 miles, this 2024 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4X offers a rare blend of off-road readiness, premium comfort, and modern technology. If youre looking for a high-end truck thats just as capable on the trail as it is on the road, this Sierra AT4X is ready to exceed expectations.
Clean CARFAX. Certified. CARFAX One-Owner.

2024 Ford F-250 Super Duty Lariat Crew Cab 4x4 in Agate Black — a high-capability heavy-duty truck built for power, towing, and premium comfort. Powered by the 6.7L High Output Power Stroke Turbo Diesel paired with a 10-speed TorqShift automatic transmission, this F-250 delivers outstanding torque, durability, and confident performance. The Lariat interior features Black Onyx leather seating, dual-zone climate control, and a massive 12" productivity screen, while the B&O premium sound system and SYNC 4 infotainment keep you connected. Factory-equipped with the High Capacity Trailer Tow Package and 5th-Wheel/Gooseneck prep, plus a 360-degree camera and advanced driver assistance features, this Super Duty is ready for serious work without sacrificing comfort or technology.

Performance & Capability

4WD

Tailgate step

Tow hooks

Power driver and passenger seats

120V outlet

1-touch up/down front windows

Outside temperature display

Particulate air filter

Technology & Convenience

FordPass Connect 5G Wi-Fi hotspot

SiriusXM with 360L

360-degree camera system

BLIS with Cross-Traffic Alert

Pre-Collision Assist with Automatic Emergency Braking

Reverse sensing system

AdvanceTrac with Roll Stability Control

Safety Canopy side curtain airbags

SOS Post-Crash Alert System

SecuriCode keyless keypad

Advanced Security Package

description:
Experience the ultimate in off-road capability and luxury with the 2024 GMC Hummer EV Pickup 3X. This remarkable electric vehicle combines impressive power, advanced technology, and uncompromising comfort to deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Tailored to the needs of the adventurous driver, this Hummer EV Pickup boasts an impressive array of premium features:

• Extreme Off-Road Package
• Infinity Roof with Removable Transparent Sky Panels
• Driver-Selectable Front and Rear Differentials
• Black Rear Recovery Hooks
• Rocker Protectors with Assist Steps
• Underbody Cameras
• 18" Black Aluminum Wheels with Machined Accents

Beneath the bold, distinctive exterior lies a powerful electric powertrain that delivers an exceptional 59 MPGe in the city and 48 MPGe on the highway. With a range of up to 329 miles, you can venture off the beaten path without worry, exploring the great outdoors with confidence.

The interior of the Hummer EV Pickup 3X is a sanctuary of comfort and technology. Sink into the premium leather-alternative seating surfaces, which offer 12-way power adjustability, heating, and ventilation for both the driver and front passenger. The Bose Centerpoint Premium 14-speaker surround sound system provides an immersive audio experience, while the intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected on the go.

Safety and convenience are paramount, with features like the Rear Camera, Adaptive Suspension, and Electronic Stability Control ensuring a secure and composed ride, no matter the terrain. The Extreme Off-Road Package further enhances the Hummer EV Pickup's capabilities, equipping it with 18-inch black aluminum wheels, LT305/70R18 Goodyear Wrangler Territory MT tires, and a suite of underbody protection and recovery features.

This 2024 GMC Hummer EV Pickup 3X in Meteorite Metallic Gray is a true testament to the brand's commitment to innovation and performance. Experience the power, versatility, and luxury of this remarkable electric vehicle for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how the Hummer EV Pickup can elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Experience the pinnacle of power and capability with the 2024 GMC Sierra 2500HD Denali Ultimate. This exceptional heavy-duty pickup is engineered to conquer any challenge, whether you're towing a massive trailer or tackling the toughest off-road terrain.

Standout features include:
• Gooseneck/5th Wheel Prep Package
• Rear Underseat Storage
• Preferred Equipment Group 5SB
• Technology Package
• X31 Off-Road Package

Beneath the bold Denali styling, this Sierra 2500HD is powered by the legendary Duramax 6.6L V8 Turbodiesel engine, delivering exceptional torque and towing capacity. Paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, you'll have the confidence to take on any job or adventure.

The premium interior of the Denali Ultimate is a masterful blend of luxury and functionality. Heated and ventilated leather seats, a heated steering wheel, and a premium Bose audio system create an unparalleled driving experience. The intuitive GMC Infotainment System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety and convenience features abound, including a Heads-Up Display, Surround Vision camera system, and a wealth of advanced driver assistance technologies. The Trailer Camera Provisions and Trailer Viewing Software make towing a breeze, while the Trailer Tire Pressure Monitor Sensors provide added peace of mind.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or embarking on epic adventures, the 2024 GMC Sierra 2500HD Denali Ultimate is the ultimate heavy-duty pickup. Experience the power, capability, and refined luxury that set this exceptional vehicle apart. Visit our showroom today to take a closer look and discover how the Sierra 2500HD Denali Ultimate can transform your driving experience.

This 2017 Ford F-350SD King Ranch is a true workhorse, engineered to conquer any task with uncompromising capability and refined comfort. Boasting a powerful 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged engine, this truck is ready to tackle your toughest jobs with ease. Equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced features, this F-350 is the ultimate companion for both work and play.

Key highlights include:
• 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged engine

The King Ranch Ultimate Package elevates this F-350 to new levels of luxury and convenience. Enjoy the twin panel power moonroof, Blind Spot Information System, and the Tailgate Step & Handle for effortless access to the bed. The FX4 Off-Road Package further enhances the truck's capabilities, with Rancho-branded shocks and skid plates to conquer any terrain.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or seeking a capable and comfortable daily driver, this 2017 Ford F-350SD King Ranch is the perfect choice. Its impressive combination of power, technology, and premium features make it a true standout in the heavy-duty truck segment.

Experience the unparalleled capability and refined luxury of this exceptional F-350 for yourself. Visit CASTLE ROCK FORD or call for your V.I.P. appointment at 720-733-7057. Price does not include Tax, Title and Fees.

2010 Hyundai Santa Fe SE – Clean Title | Spacious & Reliable SUV

The 2010 Hyundai Santa Fe SE is the perfect blend of power, style, and versatility. Designed for both comfort and performance, this SUV is powered by a 3.5L V6 engine, delivering 276 horsepower and 248 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, it offers a smooth and responsive driving experience, making it ideal for both city and highway driving.

Step inside and enjoy a spacious interior designed for comfort and convenience. The Santa Fe SE provides ample legroom and cargo space, making it a great choice for families, road trips, or everyday commuting. The premium interior materials add to its refined feel, while Bluetooth hands-free connectivity allows you to stay connected safely on the go.

Equipped with stylish alloy wheels, this SUV boasts a sleek exterior design that stands out wherever you drive. Safety is a top priority, featuring electronic stability control, traction control, and multiple airbags, ensuring peace of mind for you and your passengers.

If you're looking for a reliable and well-equipped SUV with a clean title, the 2010 Hyundai Santa Fe SE is an excellent choice. Contact us today or visit our dealership for a test drive!

description:
Discover the ultimate in power, capability, and comfort with this exceptional 2023 Ford F-250SD Platinum. This heavy-duty pickup is engineered to handle the toughest jobs with ease, while providing a premium driving experience that will impress even the most discerning buyer.

Highlighted features include:

• Sunroof Moonroof
• Bluetooth, Hands-Free
• Keyless Entry
• Backup Camera
• Leather Seats
• 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged (Power Stroke)
• Twin Panel Power Moonroof
• High Capacity 11.6" Axle Upgrade Package
• FX4 Off-Road Package
• Electronic-Locking w/3.31 Axle Ratio
• Connected Navigation
• SYNC 4 w/Enhanced Voice Recognition
• Front dual zone A/C
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel memory
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Off-Road Specifically Tuned Shock Absorbers

Powered by the legendary 6.7L Power Stroke V8 diesel engine, this F-250SD Platinum delivers exceptional performance and towing capacity. With 10-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, you'll conquer any terrain with confidence. The FX4 Off-Road Package further enhances the vehicle's off-road capabilities, ensuring you can tackle the most challenging job sites or weekend adventures.

Inside, the premium Platinum trim level surrounds you in luxury. Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone climate control, remote keyless entry, and a host of advanced technology features, including the SYNC 4 infotainment system with enhanced voice recognition. The twin-panel power moonroof and leather-wrapped steering wheel with memory function add an extra touch of refinement.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or simply seeking a capable and comfortable daily driver, this 2023 Ford F-250SD Platinum is the perfect choice. Experience the unparalleled power, versatility, and premium amenities that make this truck a true standout in its class. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive and discover how it can elevate your driving experience.

New Price -- 2023 Ford F-350 Super Duty Lariat 4X4 – Gold Certified | Ultimate Capability Meets Luxury

This 2023 Ford F-350 Lariat 4X4 delivers the perfect combination of heavy-duty performance, advanced towing technology, and premium comfort. Backed by a Clean CARFAX®, One-Owner history with No Accidents Reported, this Super Duty is built to work hard while keeping you and your passengers comfortable on every drive.

Equipped with the Lariat Ultimate Package, this F-350 offers upscale features and cutting-edge technology throughout the cabin. The Twin Panel Power Moonroof floods the interior with natural light, while Connected Navigation and the Rear View Camera make every trip more convenient. Safety and confidence come standard thanks to BLIS® with Cross-Traffic Alert, Front Sensing System, Electronic Stability Control, and Traction Control.

Designed for serious towing and hauling, this truck includes the Tow Technology Package and Camper Package, making it an excellent choice for job sites, trailers, or weekend adventures. The 18-inch alloy wheels complete the rugged yet refined exterior look.

Inside, enjoy premium comfort with power driver and passenger seats, heated and ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, and the immersive B&O Unleashed Sound System. Convenience features like Remote Keyless Entry, ABS brakes, and advanced driver-assist systems further enhance the driving experience.

12-Month/12,000-Mile Comprehensive Warranty

7-Year/100,000-Mile Powertrain Limited Warranty

172-Point Inspection & Reconditioning

24/7 Roadside Assistance

We make buying easy with No Hassle, No Haggle, Up Front Pricing—a new way of purchasing a vehicle.
We want your trade! Experience the power, luxury, and peace of mind of this 2023 Ford F-350 Lariat 4X4 today.

description: This 2023 Ford F-250 Super Duty Lariat Crew Cab is the perfect combination of heavy-duty performance, modern technology, and premium comfort, making it an exceptional choice for anyone who needs serious capability without sacrificing luxury. Finished in classic Oxford White and offered as a one-owner vehicle with a clean Carfax, this F-250 stands out as a well-cared-for diesel truck thats built to work hard and drive comfortably.Under the hood is Fords legendary 6.7L Power Stroke Turbo Diesel V8, producing a massive 475 horsepower and an incredible 1,050 lb-ft of torque. This engine delivers effortless acceleration, outstanding towing power, and rock-solid reliability whether youre hauling equipment, pulling a large trailer, or cruising the highway. Paired with 4WD, an electronic-locking rear differential, and the FX4 Off-Road Package, this truck is ready for tough job sites, back roads, and all-weather driving. While heavy-duty trucks are not EPA rated, owners typically report real-world highway fuel economy in the 1620 MPG range, which is impressive for a truck of this size and capability.Inside, the Lariat trim provides a true luxury experience. Youll enjoy premium leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, memory driver seat and pedals, power-adjustable pedals, and a refined cabin designed for long drives and everyday comfort. Technology is top-tier with SYNC 4 with enhanced voice recognition, built-in navigation, SiriusXM 360L, and the premium B&O Sound System by Bang & Olufsen that delivers rich, immersive audio throughout the cabin.Safety and convenience features include blind spot monitoring, rear backup camera, auto high-beam headlights, rain-sensing wipers, electronic stability control, hill descent control, and remote keyless entry, giving you confidence in every driving situation. The engine block heater and F-250 >10K GVWR Package make this truck especially well-suited for heavy-duty use in demanding conditions.This F-250 is also equipped with off-road tuned shock absorbers, FX4 skid plates, front fog lights, and unique FX4 off-road decals, adding both rugged performance and aggressive styling. Whether youre towing, hauling, or heading off the beaten path, this truck is built to handle it all with ease.Most importantly, this F-250 has been fully inspected, runs and drives beautifully, and offers outstanding long-term value with its one-owner history, powerful diesel engine, and premium Lariat features. Finding a Super Duty with this combination of condition, performance, and comfort is rare.This vehicle is available now at Covert Ford of Hutto. Call us today at 512-759-1414 to schedule your test drive or get more information. We are conveniently located for customers in **Austin 78758, Round Rock 78665 and 78664, Georgetown 78626, 78628 and 78633, Pflugerville 78660, Killeen 76540 and 76542, Temple 76513, 76502 and 76504, Elgin 78621, Taylor 76574, Bartlett 76511, Thorndale 76577, Coupland 78615, Granger 76530, Thrall 76578, Liberty Hill 78642, Leander 78641 and 78646, Jarrell 76537, and Cedar Park 78613 and 78630 come out today and be a part of the Covert family.

description: Introducing the 2023 Ford F-250 Super Duty Lariat TREMOR Sport Package with a High Output engine and a panoramic roof, a truck that's not just built to handle the toughest jobs, but also designed to turn heads while doing it. This powerhouse of a vehicle combines rugged capability with modern luxury, making it the ultimate choice for those who demand both performance and style. Dressed in a pristine white exterior, the F-250 exudes an aura of sophistication and strength. This truck is more than just a workhorse, it's a statement on wheels. The robust and commanding stance is complemented by Ford's award-winning design, recognized by Kelley Blue Book's Brand Image Awards for Best Styling Brand. This accolade isn't just a testament to its good looks, but a promise of the quality and innovation that Ford consistently delivers. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a cabin that redefines comfort and luxury in the world of heavy-duty trucks. The black leather interior is not only sleek and stylish but also incredibly comfortable, providing a plush environment for both driver and passengers. The attention to detail is evident in every stitch, making every drive a first-class experience. Under the hood lies the heart of this beast – the Power Stroke 6.7L Biodiesel Turbo V8 engine, delivering an awe-inspiring 500 horsepower and a staggering 1200 ft. lbs. of torque. This engine doesn't just promise power, it delivers it in spades, ensuring that no task is too big and no road is too tough. Paired with a 10-Speed Shiftable Automatic transmission, the F-250 offers seamless shifting and optimal performance, whether you're hauling heavy loads or cruising down the highway. The TREMOR Sport Package takes this truck's capability to the next level. Designed for those who crave adventure, it enhances off-road performance while maintaining the smooth ride quality Ford is known for. Whether you're navigating city streets or tackling rugged terrains, the F-250 TREMOR is equipped to handle it all with ease and grace. One of the standout features of this model is the panoramic roof, which floods the cabin with natural light and offers breathtaking views of the sky above. It's the perfect touch for those who appreciate the finer things in life and want to enjoy every journey to the fullest. In a world where trucks are often judged by their utility, the 2023 Ford F-250 Super Duty Lariat TREMOR Sport Package stands out by offering a perfect blend of power, luxury, and style. It's a truck that doesn't just meet expectations – it surpasses them, setting a new standard for what a heavy-duty vehicle can be. Don't miss the opportunity to own a truck that embodies the spirit of adventure and the promise of performance. The 2023 Ford F-250 Super Duty Lariat is ready to take on any challenge and look incredible while doing it. Experience the difference today and drive home in a vehicle that's as unstoppable as you are.
